PER TROVARE GLI ERRORI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #ERRORE#
PER TROVARE I WARNING, CERCARE LA STRINGA #WARNING#
PER TROVARE I DUPLICATI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #DUPLICATO#
*******************************************************

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_PERIODO CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_NUMERATORE CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   R_SERIE CHAR(2),
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   DATA_INZ DATETIME,
   DATA_FINE DATETIME,
   GEN_AUTOM_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   RIEL_GIA_ARCHIV CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   TIPO_ELABORAZ CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   TIPO_DIAGNOSTICA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_PERIODO CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_NUMERATORE CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   R_SERIE CHAR(2),
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   DATA_INZ DATETIME,
   DATA_FINE DATETIME,
   GEN_AUTOM_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   RIEL_GIA_ARCHIV CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   TIPO_ELABORAZ CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   TIPO_DIAGNOSTICA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CHIAVE_PRIM ON THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_STORICO ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID_AZIENDA, ID_STORICO)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOST_RES
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_RIGA INTEGER NOT NULL,
   BATCH_JOB_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ID_ANNO_DOC CHAR(6),
   ID_NUMERO_DOC CHAR(10),
   STATO_STP_DOC CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   STATO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'A',
   R_DOC_DGT BIGINT,
   R_VER_DGT SMALLINT,
   STATO_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(15),
   STATO_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(15),
   STATO_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   ESITO_PRE VARCHAR(500),
   AZIONE_POSSIBILE CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   AZIONE_ESEGUITA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ESITO_POST VARCHAR(500),
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)

Tablespace non specificato per la tabella, usato quello di default.
CREATE TABLE THIP.SOST_RES
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_RIGA INTEGER NOT NULL,
   BATCH_JOB_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ID_ANNO_DOC CHAR(6),
   ID_NUMERO_DOC CHAR(10),
   STATO_STP_DOC CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   STATO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'A',
   R_DOC_DGT BIGINT,
   R_VER_DGT SMALLINT,
   STATO_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(15),
   STATO_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(15),
   STATO_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   ESITO_PRE VARCHAR(500),
   AZIONE_POSSIBILE CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   AZIONE_ESEGUITA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ESITO_POST VARCHAR(500),
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX SOST_RES_PK ON THIP.SOST_RES (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_STORICO ASC, ID_RIGA ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.SOST_RES ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID_AZIENDA, ID_STORICO, ID_RIGA)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.SOST_RES TO PUBLIC

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BTSBPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT
(
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   DIZUTCRE CHAR(8),
   DIZDTCRE DATETIME,
   DIZHHCRE DATETIME,
   DIZUTAGG CHAR(8),
   DIZDTAGG DATETIME,
   DIZHHAGG DATETIME,
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   TT01CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   T40CD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   TSBDATA DATETIME NOT NULL,
   TSBSALDO NUMERIC(17,2),
   T29CD CHAR(4)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT ADD CONSTRAINT BTSBPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, TT01CD, T40CD, TSBDATA )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BTSBPT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.TYRTBPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.TYRTBPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.TYRTBPT
(
   WPRBNLOG NUMERIC(9,0) NOT NULL,
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T96CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   TT01CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   TT01DSNOR CHAR(35),
   T40CD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   T40DSNOR CHAR(35),
   T29CD CHAR(4),
   YRTBSATE NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSTNR NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBNR NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBCA NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBEF NUMERIC(17,2),

   YRTBDELT NUMERIC(17,2)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35658/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BTFINVG 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BTFINVG AS 
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.TT01CD,
    T1.T40CD
FROM FINANCE.BBT40VL T1 
INNER JOIN FINANCE.BTT05PT T2 ON T1.TT05CD = T2.TT05CD
WHERE T2.TT05CALI >= '20'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35726/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.GWWS1V01 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.GWWS1V01 (
    GWS1NRLG,
    T01CD,
    T96CD,
    T96DSNOR,
    T96DSRID,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZFLGPD,
    DIZTIPEL,
    DIZTIPST,
    DIZESBCH,
    GT02CD,
    GT02DSNO,
    GAT0CD,
    GAT0DSNO,
    GT03CD,
    GT03DSNO,
    GAT1CD,
    GAT1DSNO,
    GAT2CD,
    GAT2DSNO,
    GS01CD,
    GWS1OGQ2,
    GWS1OGQ3,
    GWS1OGQ4,
    GWS1OGQ5,
    GC25DSNO,
    GWS1DNQ2,
    GWS1DNQ3,
    GWS1DNQ4,
    GWS1DNQ5,
    GC34CHTO,
    GT01CD,
    GC34CD,
    GC34DSNO,
    GC34DSBR,
    GC36CD,
    GC36DSBR,
    GC36DSNO,
    T97CD,
    REASST01,
    REASST96,
    REASSSTP,
    REASDSTP,
    GFL0CDFL,
    GFL0DSFL
) AS

SELECT
    T1.GWS1NRLG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.GT02CD,
    T1.GT02DSNO,
    T1.GAT0CD,
    T1.GAT0DSNO,
    T1.GT03CD,
    T1.GT03DSNO,
    T1.GAT1CD,
    T1.GAT1DSNO,
    T1.GAT2CD,
    T1.GAT2DSNO,
    T1.GS01CD,
    T1.GWS1OGQ2,
    T1.GWS1OGQ3,
    T1.GWS1OGQ4,
    T1.GWS1OGQ5,
    T1.GC25DSNO,
    T1.GWS1DNQ2,
    T1.GWS1DNQ3,
    T1.GWS1DNQ4,
    T1.GWS1DNQ5,
    T1.GC34CHTO,
    T1.GT01CD,
    T1.GC34CD,
    T3.GC34DSNO,
    T3.GC34DSBR,
    T1.GC36CD,
    T4.GC36DSBR,
    T4.GC36DSNO,
    T1.T97CD,
    T1.REASST01,
    T1.REASST96,
    T1.REASSSTP,
    T5.STPDSNOR,
    T1.GFL0CDFL,
    T6.GFL0DSFL
FROM
      FINANCE.GWWS1PT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GFL0PT T6
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T6.GT01CD AND
         T1.GFL0CDFL = T6.GFL0CDFL
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.SVSTPPT T5
     ON  T1.REASST01 = T5.T01CD AND
         T1.REASST96 = T5.T96CD AND
         T1.REASSSTP = T5.STPCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GC36PT T4
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T4.GT01CD AND
         T1.GC36CD = T4.GC36CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GC34PT T3
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T3.GT01CD AND
         T1.GC34CD = T3.GC34CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BNCV1V2 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BNCV1V2 (
    NCV1NRIG,
    NCV0NRIG,
    T01CD,
    CLICD,
    FORCD,
    NCV1DTAZ,
    NCV1HHAZ,
    NCV1TESI,
    NCV1FLIC,
    NCV1OBJ,
    NCV1DTNC,
    NCV1HHNC,
    NCV1NOTA,
    NCV1HTM,
    NCV1RUDG,
    ANRININT,
    ANACD,
    ANRCD,
    ANRNOCON
) AS

SELECT
    T1.NCV1NRIG,
    T1.NCV0NRIG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.NCV1DTAZ,
    T1.NCV1HHAZ,
    T1.NCV1TESI,
    T1.NCV1FLIC,
    T1.NCV1OBJ,
    T1.NCV1DTNC,
    T1.NCV1HHNC,
    T1.NCV1NOTA,
    T1.NCV1HTM,
    T1.NCV1RUDG,
    T1.ANRININT,
    T1.ANACD,
    T1.ANRCD,
    T2.ANRNOCON
FROM
      FINANCE.BNCV1PT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBANRPT T2
     ON  T1.ANACD = T2.ANACD AND
         T1.ANRCD = T2.ANRCD

SELECT
    T1.NCV1NRIG,

    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.NCV1DTAZ,
    T1.NCV1HHAZ,
    T1.NCV1TESI,
    T1.NCV1FLIC,
    T1.NCV1OBJ,
    T1.NCV1DTNC,
    T1.NCV1HHNC,
    T1.NCV1NOTA,
    T1.NCV1HTM,
    T1.NCV1RUDG,
    T1.ANRININT,
    T1.ANACD,
    T1.ANRCD,
    T2.ANRNOCON
FROM
      FINANCE.BNCV1PT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBANRPT T2
     ON  T1.ANACD = T2.ANACD AND
         T1.ANRCD = T2.ANRCD

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBANRVG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BBANRVG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBANRVG AS
	SELECT 
	T1.ANACD,
	T1.ANRCD,
	T1.ANRNOCON,
	T1.ANRFUAZI,
	T1.ANRNOLIB,
	T1.ANRTELEF,
	T1.ANRFAX,
	T1.ANRININT,
	T1.ANICD,
	T1.DIZSTATO,
	T2.R_TITOLO,
	T2.COGNOME,
	T2.NOME,
	T2.NUM_CELLULARE,
	T2.R_MANSIONE,
	T2.UNITA_ORGAN,
	T2.RESPONSABILE,
	T2.ASSISTENTE,
	T2.AZIONE_MKTNG,
	T2.DECISORE,
	T2.R_INDIRIZZO_PSN,
	T2.DATA_NASCITA,
	T2.CONIUGE,
	T2.FIGLI,
	T2.R_UTENTE_CRZ,
	T2.R_UTENTE_AGG,
	T2.TIMESTAMP_CRZ,
	T2.TIMESTAMP_AGG,
	T2.PATENTE_NUM,
	T2.ENTE_RILASCIO,
	T2.DATA_RILASCIO,
	T2.DATA_SCADENZA,
	T2.R_TIPO_PATENTE,
	T2.ID_RUB_SIST_EST
	FROM 
		FINANCE.BBANRPT T1
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT T2 
		ON T1.ANACD = T2.ID_ANAGRAFICO AND T1.ANRCD  = T2.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB

DROP VIEW FINANCE.GFL0VG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.GFL0VG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.GFL0VG AS
SELECT
    T1.GT01CD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.GFL0CDFL,
    T1.GFL0DSFL,
    T1.GFL0DSRD,
    T1.GFL0DSRC,
    T1.GFL0AUTM,
    T1.GFL0UTIL
FROM FINANCE.GFL0PT T1
WHERE T1.GFL0AUTM = '1'

    T1.YEAT33CL,
    T1.YEACDFOR,
    T1.DIATPFOR,
    T1.BYYEACFF,
    T1.CCPCOFIS,
    T1.DITIPRSF,
    T1.WEADINTE,
    CHAR(T1.YEAPROIN) AS YEAPROIN,
    T1.YEAPRDOC,
    T1.CCHCFISC,
    T1.CCHCFSSR,
    T1.T97NUTIL,
    T1.CCHCONOM,
    T1.CCHNOME,
    T1.CCHSESSO,
    T1.CCHDTNAS,
    T1.CCHCONAS,
    T1.T76CD,
    T1.CCPININT,
    T1.T79NOTA,
    T1.BYYEAPRR,
    T1.T79ANRFD,
    T1.ANACOFIS,
    T1.ANACOGNO,
    T1.ANANOME,
    T1.ANASESSO,
    T1.DITFIDIC,
    T1.WEADIVAP,
    T1.CCPTGPLI,
    T1.YEAESPOR,
    T1.YEACECEE,
    T1.YEACESMA,
    T1.YEAOPASS,
    T1.YEAOPSTR,
    T1.DITCDFIS,
    T1.DITDTIMP,
    T1.DITFIINT,
    CHAR(T1.ENCPRDIC) AS ENCPRDIC,
    T1.ENCPRDOC,
    T1.BYYEAFCO,
    T1.T79CD,
    T1.EDIPATHP,
    (
	COALESCE((SELECT SUM(A.DICIMUTI) FROM FINANCE.BCEA1PT A WHERE A.T01CD = T1.T01CD AND A.DIFANRFD = T1.DIFANRFD AND A.DIFNRPEA = T1.DIFNRPEA AND A.FORCD = T1.FORCD),0)
    ) AS DICIMUTI,
    T1.DICDTFIN, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (T1.DICDTFIN IS NULL) THEN '1'  
      WHEN (T1.DICDTFIN=CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) THEN '1' 
      ELSE '2'  END
     ) AS YEAICO1 
FROM FINANCE.BYYEAPT T1 

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCEDIVG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCEDIVG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCEDIVG AS 
SELECT
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.WEANRLOG,
    T1.ENCSTATO,
    T1.T79CD,
    T1.DIFANRFD,
    T1.DIFDTSTA,
    T1.YEACDFOR,
    T1.DIATPFOR,
    T1.DITIPRSF,
    T1.WEADINTE,
    T1.CCHCFISC,
    T1.CCHCFSSR,
    T1.DITFIDIC,
    T1.WEADIVAP,
    T1.CCPTGPLI,
    T1.YEAESPOR,
    T1.YEACECEE,
    T1.YEACESMA,
    T1.YEAOPASS,
    T1.YEAOPSTR,
    T1.DITCDFIS,
    T1.DITDTIMP,
    T1.DITFIINT,
    CHAR(T1.ENCPRDIC) AS ENCPRDIC,
    T1.ENCPRDOC,
    T1.BYYEAFCO,
    T1.EDIPATHP
FROM FINANCE.BCEDIPT T1

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36005/primrose/script/02VisteBG.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCMOTV11 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCMOTV11 AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T09CD,
    T1.MOVNUREG,
    T1.MOVTCLFO,
    T1.MOVDTDOC,
    T1.MOVNDORI,
    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.T07CD,
    T1.MOVNPIVA
FROM FINANCE.BCMOTPT T1
WHERE
  ( ( T1.MOVTCLFO = '1' ) OR  ( T1.MOVTCLFO = '2' ) )

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIXPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   RIEDTCHC DATETIME NOT NULL,
   RIENPCHC NUMERIC(3,0) NOT NULL,
   T06CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCRIXPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD,RIEDTCHC,RIENPCHC,T06CD )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCRIXPT TO PUBLIC

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCRIXVA 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIXVA' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCRIXVA (
    T01CD,
    RIEDTCHC,
    RIENPCHC,
    T06CD ) AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.RIEDTCHC,
    T1.RIENPCHC,
    T1.T06CD 
FROM FINANCE.BCRIXPT T1

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36384/tddml/DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01.tddml.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01 AS 

				SELECT DOC.*, 
				(
					CASE FAT.TIPO_DOC_ACQ_CTRL
						WHEN '3'
							THEN '(S)'
						WHEN '2'
							THEN '(T)'
						ELSE ''
					END
				) AS TIPO_DOC_ACQ_CTRL
				
				FROM THIP.DOC_ACQ_TES DOC  
				LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATACQ_DOCACQ FAT ON 
								DOC.ID_AZIENDA = FAT.ID_AZIENDA AND 
								DOC.ID_ANNO_DOC = FAT.ID_ANNO_DOC_ACQ  AND 
								DOC.ID_NUMERO_DOC  = FAT.ID_NUM_DOC_ACQ
GRANT ALL ON THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01 TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36213/tddml/IOF_PRIORITA.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.IOF_PRIORITA
CREATE VIEW
				THIP.IOF_PRIORITA
				(
				PRIORITA_EFF, ASSEGNATA_EFF, STATO_ATV, TIMESTAMP_AGG_LISTA, TIMESTAMP_AGG_ATV, TIMESTAMP_PRC_R,
				NUM_RITORNO, ID_AZIENDA, ID_ANNO_ORD, ID_NUMERO_ORD, ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN,ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, ID_PROGRESSIVO_T, ID_PROGRESSIVO_R, ID_AZIENDA_ORD

				)
				AS
				SELECT 
                LISTA.PRIORITA AS PRIORITA_EFF, LISTA.ASSEGNATA AS ASSEGNATA_EFF, ATV.STATO_ATTIV, LISTA.TIMESTAMP_AGG, 
				ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG, ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_R, ORD.NUM_RITORNO, LISTA.ID_AZIENDA,
				LISTA.ID_ANNO_ORD, LISTA.ID_NUMERO_ORD, LISTA.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, ORD.PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, ORD.LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN , ORD.ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, ORD.ID_PROGRESSIVO_T, ORD.ID_PROGRESSIVO_R, ORD.ID_AZIENDA AS ID_AZIENDA_ORD
				FROM
				
				THIP.IOF_ORDINI ORD
				LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RIL_PRD_LST_ATV LISTA ON
                (ORD.ID_AZIENDA = LISTA.ID_AZIENDA AND
                LISTA.ID_AMBIENTE = 'IOF' AND 
                ORD.R_ANNO_ORD = LISTA.ID_ANNO_ORD AND 
                ORD.R_NUMERO_ORD = LISTA.ID_NUMERO_ORD AND
                ORD.R_RIGA_ORD = LISTA.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA)
                LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.ORD_ESEC_ATV ATV ON
                (ORD.ID_AZIENDA = ATV.ID_AZIENDA AND
                ORD.R_ANNO_ORD = ATV.ID_ANNO_ORD AND 
                ORD.R_NUMERO_ORD = ATV.ID_NUMERO_ORD AND
                ORD.R_RIGA_ORD = ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA)
				WHERE
                ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG > ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_R OR
                LISTA.TIMESTAMP_AGG > ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_R OR
                ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_R IS NULL OR STATO_PRC_R = '2'

    T36CD,
    T36DSNOR,
    T36DSRID,
    VOCCD,
    VOCDSNOR,
    PNLINTRA,
    WECDTRIF
) AS

SELECT
    T1.WECNRLOG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.T01CDFIL,
    T1.T96FIL,
    T1.T97FIL,
    T1.T91FIL,
    T1.T91VLCB1,
    T1.T91VLCB2,
    T1.T91VLCB3,
    T1.T91VLCB4,
    T1.SQLSTMT,
    T1.WECDTFRG,
    T1.WECTPCMP,
    T1.WECFMVPR,
    T1.WECANFIN,
    T1.WECANINI,
    T1.WECNPINI,
    T1.WECNPFIN,
    T1.WECORDIN,
    T1.WECDTCRI,
    T1.WECDTCRF,
    T1.WECTPELS,
    T1.WECFANRG,
    T1.WECFSTRA,
    T1.WECVCOVE,
    T1.WECFLAGE,
    T1.WECFLPAG,
    T1.WECFLTPR,
    T1.WECFRBNS,
    T1.WECFANCT,
    T1.WECFSTDV,
    T1.WECCOMPE,
    T1.WECINCLP,
    T1.WECLNDEC,
    T1.WECTPVAL,
    T1.WECVAL,
    T1.T33CD,
    T1.T29CD,
    T1.T36CD,
    T3.T36DSNOR,
    T3.T36DSRID,
    T1.VOCCD,
    T4.VOCDSNOR,
    T1.PNLINTRA,
    T1.WECDTRIF
FROM
      FINANCE.BWWECPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.VOCCD = T4.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT36PT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.T36CD = T3.T36CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

CREATE VIEW FINANCE.GWWHAV1 (
    GWHANRLG,
    T01CD,
    T96CD,
    T96DSNOR,
    T96DSRID,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZFLGPD,
    DIZTIPEL,
    DIZTIPST,
    DIZESBCH,
    BWWW0016,
    BWWW0001,
    GWHACHCG,
    VOCGPAAP,
    GWHATPP,
    GWHACHCO,
    GWHASTR,
    GWHARCOL,
    MOVDTRCO,
    MOVDTCOA,
    GIPNNLOG,
    VOCCD,
    VOCDSNOR,
    VOCDSRID,
    T02CD,
    T02DSNOR,
    T02DSRID,
    GT01CD,
    GEV0CD,
    GEV0DSNO,
    GT05CD,
    GT05DSNO,
    GT05DSBR,
    T09CD,
    T09DSNOR,
    T09DSRID
) AS

SELECT
    T1.GWHANRLG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.BWWW0016,
    T1.BWWW0001,
    T1.GWHACHCG,
    T1.VOCGPAAP,
    T1.GWHATPP,
    T1.GWHACHCO,
    T1.GWHASTR,
    T1.GWHARCOL,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOVDTCOA,
    T1.GIPNNLOG,
    T1.VOCCD,
    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID,
    T1.T02CD,
    T4.T02DSNOR,
    T4.T02DSRID,
    T1.GT01CD,
    T1.GEV0CD,
    T5.GEV0DSNO,
    T1.GT05CD,
    T6.GT05DSNO,
    T6.GT05DSBR,
    T1.T09CD,
    T7.T09DSNOR,
    T7.T09DSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.GWWHAPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT09PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.T09CD = T7.T09CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GT05PT T6
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T6.GT01CD AND
         T1.GT05CD = T6.GT05CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GEV0PT T5
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T5.GT01CD AND
         T1.GEV0CD = T5.GEV0CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.T02CD = T4.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.VOCCD = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

         LEFT OUTER JOIN

     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT09PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.T09CD = T7.T09CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GT05PT T6
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T6.GT01CD AND
         T1.GT05CD = T6.GT05CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GEV0PT T5
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T5.GT01CD AND
         T1.GEV0CD = T5.GEV0CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.T02CD = T4.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.VOCCD = T3.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

T1.TACQIVADF,
( CASE  WHEN (T1.TACQFLPO='1' OR T1.TACQFLPR='1' OR T1.TACQFLCN='1') THEN '1'   ELSE '0'  END) AS TACQIC2, 
( CASE  WHEN (T1.TACQNOTE<>' ') THEN '1'   ELSE '0'  END) AS TACQIC3, 
T1.KEYINVIO, 
T1.KEY1FATT, 
T1.KEY2FATT, 
T1.PTHTISDI, 
T1.PTHANFAT, 
T1.PTHNRFAT,

T1.PTHRICON, 	   
T1.PTHCARAT, 
T1.PTHANNOT, 
T1.TACQIMPX, 
T1.TACQIVAX, 
T1.TACQTOTX, 
( CASE 
	WHEN (COALESCE(T2.KEYINVIO, ' ')<>' ' AND COALESCE(T1.TRANREGG, 0)=0) THEN '2' 
	WHEN (COALESCE(T2.KEYINVIO, ' ')<>' ' AND COALESCE(T1.TRANREGG, 0)<>0 AND (COALESCE(T1.TRANREGG, 0)<>T2.MOVNUREG OR COALESCE(T1.T09CD, ' ')<>T2.T09CD) ) THEN '2' 
	WHEN (COALESCE(T1.KEYINVIO, ' ')<>' ') THEN '1' 
	ELSE '0' END) AS TACQIC4, 
( CASE  WHEN (T1.KEYINVIO<>' ' AND (T1.TACQTFDO<>T1.TACQTOTX)) THEN '1'   ELSE '0'  END) AS TACQIC5 
FROM FINANCE.THACQPT T1 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMFEPT T2 ON 
T1.T01CD=T2.T01CD AND
T1.KEYINVIO=T2.KEYINVIO AND 
T1.KEY1FATT=T2.KEY1FATT AND 
T1.KEY2FATT=T2.KEY2FATT AND
T2.KEYINVIO IS NOT NULL AND
T2.KEYINVIO <> ' ' 

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.THACQVG TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36220/tddml/FATVEN_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.FATVEN_V01
CREATE VIEW
    THIP.FATVEN_V01
    (
        ID_AZIENDA,
        ID_ANNO_FAT,
        ID_NUMERO_FAT,
        DATA_FAT,
        R_NUM_FAT,
        COL_CONTABILITA,
        NUMERO_FAT_FMT,
        CODIFICA_SIA,
        R_ABI,
        R_CAB,
        R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
        NUM_CONTO_COR,
        CLIENTE_FATVEN,
        ID_ANNO_DOC,
        ID_NUMERO_DOC,
        R_AGENTE,
        R_CLIENTE,
        R_CLIENTE_FAT,
        R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
        STP_FATTURA,
		STATO,
		STT_INVIO_SDI,
		R_DIVISIONE,
		SERIE_FAT
    ) AS
SELECT
    C.ID_AZIENDA,
    C.ID_ANNO_FAT,
    C.ID_NUMERO_FAT,
    C.DATA_FAT,
    C.R_NUM_FAT,
    C.COL_CONTABILITA,
    C.NUMERO_FAT_FMT,
    C.CODIFICA_SIA,
    C.R_ABI,
    C.R_CAB,
    C.R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
    C.NUM_CONTO_COR,
    C.R_CLIENTE_FAT CLIENTE_FATVEN ,
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC,
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC,
    D.R_AGENTE,
    D.R_CLIENTE,
    D.R_CLIENTE_FAT,
    D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
    D.STP_FATTURA,
	C.STATO,
	C.STT_INVIO_SDI,
	C.R_DIVISIONE,
	LEFT(C.ID_NUMERO_FAT,2) SERIE_FAT
FROM
    THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V10 D,
    THIP.FATVEN C
WHERE
    C.ID_AZIENDA = D.ID_AZIENDA
AND C.ID_ANNO_FAT = D.ANNO_FAT
AND C.ID_NUMERO_FAT = D.NUMERO_FATTURA
AND D.TP_DOC_VEN <= '3'
AND D.STP_FATTURA = '2'
AND C.COL_CONTABILITA = '0'
AND C.STATO = 'V'

GRANT ALL ON THIP.FATVEN_V01 TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35350/tddml/UPDATE_ORD_ACQ_RIG_SEC.TDDML.
UPDATE THIP.ORD_ACQ_RIG SET STATO_SPED_COMP ='2', SALDO_MANUALE = 'Y'  WHERE ID_DET_RIGA_ORD > 0 AND  STATO_SPED_COMP <> '2' AND QTA_S_LVE_UM_PRM < QTA_ORD_UM_PRM AND
	(
		ID_AZIENDA + '$' +  ID_ANNO_ORD + '$' +  ID_NUMERO_ORD + '$' + CONVERT(varchar(10), ID_RIGA_ORD)  IN (SELECT ID_AZIENDA + '$' +  ID_ANNO_ORD + '$' +  ID_NUMERO_ORD + '$' + CONVERT(varchar(10), ID_RIGA_ORD)  FROM  THIP.ORD_ACQ_RIG PRM WHERE ID_DET_RIGA_ORD = 0 AND STATO_EVASIONE = '2')
	)
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


UPDATE THIP.ORD_ACQ_RIG SET STATO_SPED_COMP ='2'  WHERE ID_DET_RIGA_ORD > 0 AND  STATO_SPED_COMP <> '2' AND QTA_S_LVE_UM_PRM >= QTA_ORD_UM_PRM AND
	(
		ID_AZIENDA + '$' +  ID_ANNO_ORD + '$' +  ID_NUMERO_ORD + '$' + CONVERT(varchar(10), ID_RIGA_ORD)  IN (SELECT ID_AZIENDA + '$' +  ID_ANNO_ORD + '$' +  ID_NUMERO_ORD + '$' + CONVERT(varchar(10), ID_RIGA_ORD)  FROM  THIP.ORD_ACQ_RIG PRM WHERE ID_DET_RIGA_ORD = 0 AND STATO_EVASIONE = '2')
	)
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.

CREATE TABLE THIP.ART_REGIME_OSS
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DESCR_RIDOTTA CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   DESCRIZIONE VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL,
   STATO CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   ID_ARTICOLO CHAR(25) NOT NULL,
   ID_ASS_IVA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_NAZIONE CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_CONNOTAZ_OSS CHAR(5) NOT NULL
)

(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35745/tddml/MODPRO_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.MODPRO_V01
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.MODPRO_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         AS ID_AZIENDA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_MODELLO         AS ID_MODELLO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_STABILIMENTO     AS R_STABILIMENTO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.DOMINIO            AS DOMINIO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.PRIORITA           AS PRIORITA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO         AS R_ARTICOLO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_COMMESSA         AS R_COMMESSA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.DESCRIZIONE        AS DESCRIZIONE, 
    THIP.MODPRO.DESCR_RIDOTTA      AS DESCR_RIDOTTA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO       AS TIPO_MODELLO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.LOTTO_MINIMO       AS LOTTO_MINIMO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.LOTTO_MULTIPLO     AS LOTTO_MULTIPLO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.LOTTO_MASSIMO      AS LOTTO_MASSIMO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.LOTTO_ATTREZ       AS LOTTO_ATTREZ, 
	THIP.MODPRO.NUM_PAR_LOT_MAX    AS NUM_PAR_LOT_MAX, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MIN  AS TEMPO_APV_LOT_MIN, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MUL  AS TEMPO_APV_LOT_MUL, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TEMPI_PIANIF_APV   AS TEMPI_PIANIF_APV, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TEMPO_ANT_FAB      AS TEMPO_ANT_FAB, 
    THIP.MODPRO.QUANTITA_BASE      AS QUANTITA_BASE, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_VRS    AS R_MAGAZZINO_VRS, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL    AS R_MAGAZZINO_PRL, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_TIPO_CIC_STD     AS R_TIPO_CIC_STD, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_POLIT_RIORD      AS R_POLIT_RIORD, 
    THIP.MODPRO.DATA_DISPON        AS DATA_DISPON, 
    THIP.MODPRO.DATA_AGGIOR        AS DATA_AGGIOR, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_RESPONSABILE     AS R_RESPONSABILE, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_DOCUMENTO_MM     AS R_DOCUMENTO_MM, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_GES_COMMENTI     AS R_GES_COMMENTI, 
    THIP.MODPRO.STATO              AS STATO, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_UTENTE_AGG       AS R_UTENTE_AGG, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_UTENTE_CRZ       AS R_UTENTE_CRZ, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_CRZ      AS TIMESTAMP_CRZ, 
    THIP.MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_AGG      AS TIMESTAMP_AGG, 
    THIP.MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_WIP    AS R_MAGAZZINO_WIP,
	THIP.MODPRO.METODO_RES_ORD     AS METODO_RES_ORD,
	THIP.MODPRO.R_CLIENTE          AS R_CLIENTE,
    THIP.MODPRO.STATO_COMPLETAM_ORD    AS STATO_COMPLETAM_ORD,
    THIP.ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO      AS ID_ARTICOLO, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.DESCRIZIONE      AS ART_DESCRIZIONE, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.DESCR_RIDOTTA    AS ART_DESCR_RIDOTTA, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.TIPO_PARTE       AS TIPO_PARTE, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_GRP_MODELLO    AS R_GRP_MODELLO, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_UM_TECNICA     AS R_UM_TECNICA, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_UM_PRM_MAG     AS R_UM_PRM_MAG, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_CATEGORIA_UM   AS R_CATEGORIA_UM, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_SCHEMA_CFG     AS R_SCHEMA_CFG, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.EREDITA_CFG      AS EREDITA_CFG, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.R_CONFIG_STD     AS R_CONFIG_STD, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.GES_SALDI_COMMES AS GES_SALDI_COMMES, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI.QTA_INTERA       AS QTA_INTERA    
FROM 
    THIP.MODPRO, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI 
WHERE 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA     = THIP.ARTICOLI.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO = THIP.ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO

CREATE VIEW THIP.IMPLOSIONE_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA,MODPRO.ID_MODELLO,MODPRO.R_STABILIMENTO,MODPRO.DOMINIO,MODPRO.PRIORITA,MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO,MODPRO.R_COMMESSA,MODPRO.DESCRIZIONE,MODPRO.DESCR_RIDOTTA,MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MINIMO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MULTIPLO,MODPRO.LOTTO_MASSIMO,MODPRO.LOTTO_ATTREZ,MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MIN,MODPRO.TEMPO_APV_LOT_MUL,MODPRO.TEMPI_PIANIF_APV,MODPRO.TEMPO_ANT_FAB,MODPRO.QUANTITA_BASE,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_VRS,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL,MODPRO.R_TIPO_CIC_STD,MODPRO.R_POLIT_RIORD,MODPRO.DATA_DISPON,MODPRO.DATA_AGGIOR,MODPRO.R_RESPONSABILE,MODPRO.R_DOCUMENTO_MM,MODPRO.R_GES_COMMENTI,MODPRO.STATO,MODPRO.R_UTENTE_AGG,MODPRO.R_UTENTE_CRZ,MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_CRZ,MODPRO.TIMESTAMP_AGG,MODPRO.R_MAGAZZINO_WIP,MODPRO.METODO_RES_ORD,MODPRO.R_CLIENTE,MODPRO.NUM_PAR_LOT_MAX, MODPRO.STATO_COMPLETAM_ORD,
    M_ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO      AS M_ID_ARTICOLO, 
    M_ARTICOLI.DESCRIZIONE      AS M_ART_DESCRIZIONE, 
    M_ARTICOLI.DESCR_RIDOTTA    AS M_ART_DESCR_RIDOTTA, 
    M_ARTICOLI.TIPO_PARTE       AS M_TIPO_PARTE, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_GRP_MODELLO    AS M_R_GRP_MODELLO, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_UM_TECNICA     AS M_R_UM_TECNICA, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_UM_PRM_MAG     AS M_R_UM_PRM_MAG, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_CATEGORIA_UM   AS M_R_CATEGORIA_UM, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_SCHEMA_CFG     AS M_R_SCHEMA_CFG, 
    M_ARTICOLI.EREDITA_CFG      AS M_EREDITA_CFG, 
    M_ARTICOLI.R_CONFIG_STD     AS M_R_CONFIG_STD, 
    M_ARTICOLI.GES_SALDI_COMMES AS M_GES_SALDI_COMM, 
    M_ARTICOLI.QTA_INTERA       AS M_QTA_INTERA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DESCRIZIONE   AS ATV_DESC, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DESCR_RIDOTTA AS ATV_DESC_R, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_ATTIVITA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_OPERAZIONE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_CENTRO_LAVORO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_CENTRO_COSTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_ATTREZZAGGIO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.SOG_COLLAUDO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.BUFFER_ANTICIPO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TEMPO_SOVRAP, 
    MODPRO_ATV.QUANTITA_SOVRAP, 
    MODPRO_ATV.NUM_PARALLELISMO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.LOTTO_MOVIM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.REINTEGRO_SCARTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.PERCEN_SCARTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIPO_CRIT_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DATA_INZ_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.DATA_FIN_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_VER_INZ_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_VER_FIN_VALID, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_REGOLA, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIPI_CICLO_AMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.SINTESI_TIPI_CICLO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.VINCOLO_DATA_PGM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.POL_CONS_ATTIV, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_LAV, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_PRL, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_BOLLA_VRS, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STP_TAGLND_IDENT, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_GES_COMMENTI AS ATV_GES_COMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_DOCUMENTO_MM AS ATV_DOC_MM, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ATV_INIZIALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.ATV_FINALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV.STATO         AS ATV_STATO, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_UTENTE_CRZ  AS ATV_UT_CR, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIMESTAMP_CRZ AS ATV_TS_CR, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG AS ATV_TS_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV.R_UTENTE_AGG  AS ATV_UT_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV.TIPO_ATTIVITA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA AS MAT_RIG_ATV, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.DESCRIZIONE   AS MAT_DESC, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.DESCR_RIDOTTA AS MAT_DESC_R, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.SEQUENZA_ORDIN, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO AS MAT_ART, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_VERSIONE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_CONFIGURAZIONE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_COMMESSA AS MAT_COMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COEFF_IMPIEGO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COEFF_TOTALE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.PERCEN_SCARTO   AS ATV_PERC_SC, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIPO_CRIT_VALID AS MAT_CRIT, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.DATA_INZ_VALID  AS MAT_DATA_INZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.DATA_FIN_VALID  AS MAT_DATA_FIN, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_VER_INZ_VALID AS MAT_VER_INZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_VER_FIN_VALID AS MAT_VER_FIN, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_REGOLA        AS MAT_REGOLA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UM_DIMENSIONI, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.LUNGHEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.LARGHEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ALTEZZA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COEFF_TAGLIO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.BUFFER_ANTICIPO AS MAT_BUF_ANT, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.MOD_PRELIEVO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL AS MAT_MAG_PRL, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO_ALT, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.NOTE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.STATO         AS MAT_STATO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UTENTE_AGG  AS MAT_UT_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_UTENTE_CRZ  AS MAT_UT_CRZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIMESTAMP_CRZ AS MAT_TS_CRZ, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIMESTAMP_AGG AS MAT_TS_AGG, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ESPONI_IN_BOLLA, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.APPLIC_ANTICIPO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.IDENTIF_BENE  AS IDENTIF_BENE, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ADDEBITO_SER  AS ADDEBITO_SER, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.RIFERIMENTO   AS RIFERIMENTO, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_SCHEMA_CFG  AS R_SCHEMA_COEFF, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MACRO_COEFF AS R_MACRO_COEFF, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ESCLUSO_COSTI AS ESCLUSO_COSTI, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.COSTO_LOT_ATTREZ AS COSTO_LOT_ATTREZ, 
	MODPRO_ATV_MAT.TIPI_CICLO_AMM AS MAT_TP_CIC_AMM, 
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.SINTESI_TIPI_CICLO AS MAT_SINT_TP_CIC,
    MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_RFR AS R_MAGAZZINO_RFR,
    ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO         AS ID_ARTICOLO, 
    ARTICOLI.DESCRIZIONE         AS ART_DESCRIZIONE, 
    ARTICOLI.DESCR_RIDOTTA       AS ART_DESCR_RIDOTTA, 
    ARTICOLI.TIPO_PARTE          AS TIPO_PARTE, 
    ARTICOLI.R_GRP_MODELLO       AS R_GRP_MODELLO, 
    ARTICOLI.R_UM_TECNICA        AS R_UM_TECNICA, 
    ARTICOLI.R_UM_PRM_MAG        AS R_UM_PRM_MAG, 
    ARTICOLI.R_CATEGORIA_UM      AS R_CATEGORIA_UM, 
    ARTICOLI.R_SCHEMA_CFG        AS R_SCHEMA_CFG, 
    ARTICOLI.EREDITA_CFG         AS EREDITA_CFG, 
    ARTICOLI.R_CONFIG_STD        AS R_CONFIG_STD, 
    ARTICOLI.GES_SALDI_COMMES    AS GES_SALDI_COMMES, 
    ARTICOLI.QTA_INTERA          AS QTA_INTERA,
    M_ARTICOLI.GES_VERSIONI AS GES_VERSIONI
FROM THIP.MODPRO MODPRO,THIP.ARTICOLI M_ARTICOLI,THIP.MODPRO_ATV MODPRO_ATV,THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT MODPRO_ATV_MAT,THIP.ARTICOLI ARTICOLI 
WHERE 
    MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA               = M_ARTICOLI.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = MODPRO_ATV.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA           = ARTICOLI.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO           = M_ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO 
    AND MODPRO.ID_MODELLO           = MODPRO_ATV.ID_MODELLO 
    AND MODPRO.ID_MODELLO           = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_MODELLO 
    AND MODPRO_ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA = MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA 
    AND MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO   = ARTICOLI.ID_ARTICOLO

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35943/tddml/IOF_PRIORITA.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.IOF_PRIORITA
CREATE VIEW
				THIP.IOF_PRIORITA
				(
				PRIORITA_EFF, ASSEGNATA_EFF, STATO_ATV, TIMESTAMP_AGG_LISTA, TIMESTAMP_AGG_ATV, TIMESTAMP_PRC_T,
				NUM_RITORNO, ID_AZIENDA, ID_ANNO_ORD, ID_NUMERO_ORD, ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN,ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, ID_PROGRESSIVO_T, ID_PROGRESSIVO_R, ID_AZIENDA_ORD

				)
				AS
				SELECT 
                LISTA.PRIORITA AS PRIORITA_EFF, LISTA.ASSEGNATA AS ASSEGNATA_EFF, ATV.STATO_ATTIV, LISTA.TIMESTAMP_AGG, 
				ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG, ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_T, ORD.NUM_RITORNO, LISTA.ID_AZIENDA,
				LISTA.ID_ANNO_ORD, LISTA.ID_NUMERO_ORD, LISTA.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, ORD.PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, ORD.LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN , ORD.ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, ORD.ID_PROGRESSIVO_T, ORD.ID_PROGRESSIVO_R, ORD.ID_AZIENDA AS ID_AZIENDA_ORD
				FROM
				
				THIP.IOF_ORDINI ORD
				LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RIL_PRD_LST_ATV LISTA ON
                (ORD.ID_AZIENDA = LISTA.ID_AZIENDA AND
                LISTA.ID_AMBIENTE = 'IOF' AND 
                ORD.R_ANNO_ORD = LISTA.ID_ANNO_ORD AND 
                ORD.R_NUMERO_ORD = LISTA.ID_NUMERO_ORD AND
                ORD.R_RIGA_ORD = LISTA.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA)
                LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.ORD_ESEC_ATV ATV ON
                (ORD.ID_AZIENDA = ATV.ID_AZIENDA AND
                ORD.R_ANNO_ORD = ATV.ID_ANNO_ORD AND 
                ORD.R_NUMERO_ORD = ATV.ID_NUMERO_ORD AND
                ORD.R_RIGA_ORD = ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA)
				WHERE
                ATV.TIMESTAMP_AGG > ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_T OR
                LISTA.TIMESTAMP_AGG > ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_T OR
                ORD.TIMESTAMP_PRC_T IS NULL

#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCBCTDPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BCBCTDPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   T33CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DIZDESLI CHAR(35),
   DIZDRILI CHAR(15),
   SBCCSDBC CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   BC1NATCO CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   BC1SZBIL CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   BC1COLN1 CHAR(9) NOT NULL,
   BC2COLN2 CHAR(9) NOT NULL,
   BC3COLN3 CHAR(9) NOT NULL,
   BC4COLN4 CHAR(9) NOT NULL,
   BC5COLN5 CHAR(9) NOT NULL,
   BCTNPRGT NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   BCTESDES VARCHAR(256)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCBCTDPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCBCTDPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, T33CD, SBCCSDBC, BC1NATCO, BC1SZBIL, BC1COLN1, BC2COLN2, BC3COLN3, BC4COLN4, BC5COLN5, BCTNPRGT )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCBCTDPT TO PUBLIC
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BWWBSPT ADD    T33CD CHAR(3)
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BWWBSPT ADD    WBSSBCDS VARCHAR(35)
UPDATE FINANCE.BWWBSPT SET T33CD=' ' WHERE T33CD IS NULL 
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


UPDATE FINANCE.BWWBSPT SET WBSSBCDS = (SELECT SBCDSNOR FROM FINANCE.BCSBCPT A WHERE A.T01CD = FINANCE.BWWBSPT.T01CD AND A.SBCCSDBC = FINANCE.BWWBSPT.SBCCSDBC ) 
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


UPDATE FINANCE.BWWBSPT SET WBSSBCDS=' ' WHERE WBSSBCDS IS NULL 
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BWWBSPT TO PUBLIC

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBPD1DVA 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBPD1DVA AS
SELECT
    T1.PDCDS1ES,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T51CD,
    T1.PDCCONL1,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.T33CD,
    T1.DIZDESLI,
    T1.DIZDRILI
FROM FINANCE.BBPD1DPT T1

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BWWBEV1 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BWWBEV1 (
    WBENRLOG,
    T01CD,
    T96CD,
    T96DSNOR,
    T96DSRID,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZFLGPD,
    DIZTIPEL,
    DIZTIPST,
    DIZESBCH,
    WBEDTELB,
    WBEDTIRG,
    WBEDTFRG,
    WBEESELA,
    WBETPVAL,
    WBEFMVPR,
    WBEFANCT,
    WBEFNATV,
    WBELIVCO,
    WBEFSPAT,
    WBEFDEVO,
    WBEFCSZ,
    WBEDTALT,
    WBESOVES,
    WBEFSTES,
    WBEELDIV,
    WBECLIFO,
    WBEDTGCF,
    T51CD,
    WBEFRCSL,
    T33CD
) AS

SELECT
    T1.WBENRLOG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.WBEDTELB,
    T1.WBEDTIRG,
    T1.WBEDTFRG,
    T1.WBEESELA,
    T1.WBETPVAL,
    T1.WBEFMVPR,
    T1.WBEFANCT,
    T1.WBEFNATV,
    T1.WBELIVCO,
    T1.WBEFSPAT,
    T1.WBEFDEVO,
    T1.WBEFCSZ,
    T1.WBEDTALT,
    T1.WBESOVES,
    T1.WBEFSTES,
    T1.WBEELDIV,
    T1.WBECLIFO,
    T1.WBEDTGCF,
    T1.T51CD,
    T1.WBEFRCSL,
    T1.T33CD
FROM
      FINANCE.BWWBEPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD
    

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BWWBEVA

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BWWBSV1 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BWWBSV1 (
    WBSNRLOG,
    T01CD,
    T96CD,
    T96DSNOR,
    T96DSRID,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZFLGPD,
    DIZTIPEL,
    DIZTIPST,
    DIZESBCH,
    WBSTPVAL,
    WBSNATCO,
    WBSTPSTP,
    WBSINCMR,
    WBSTOTAT,
    WBSTOTPA,
    WBSSTANS,
    WBSNODEC,
    WSBDECOD,
    WBSFVCSZ,
    SBCCSDBC,
    SBCDSNOR,
    T64COPBC,
    T64DESNO,
    WBSCDPER,
    WBSDSPER,
    T36CD,
    T36DSNOR,
    T36CD2,
    T36DSNR2,
    T33CD,
    WBSSBCDS
) AS

SELECT
    T1.WBSNRLOG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.WBSTPVAL,
    T1.WBSNATCO,
    T1.WBSTPSTP,
    T1.WBSINCMR,
    T1.WBSTOTAT,
    T1.WBSTOTPA,
    T1.WBSSTANS,
    T1.WBSNODEC,
    T1.WSBDECOD,
    T1.WBSFVCSZ,
    T1.SBCCSDBC,
    T3.SBCDSNOR,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T4.T64DESNO,
    T1.WBSCDPER,
    T5.T64DESNO,
    T1.T36CD,
    T6.T36DSNOR,
    T1.T36CD2,
    T7.T36DSNOR,
    T1.T33CD,
    T1.WBSSBCDS
FROM
      FINANCE.BWWBSPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT36PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.T36CD2 = T7.T36CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT36PT T6
     ON  T1.T01CD = T6.T01CD AND
         T1.T36CD = T6.T36CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT64PT T5
     ON  T1.T01CD = T5.T01CD AND
         T1.WBSCDPER = T5.T64COPBC
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT64PT T4
     ON  T1.T01CD = T4.T01CD AND
         T1.T64COPBC = T4.T64COPBC
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BCSBCPT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.SBCCSDBC = T3.SBCCSDBC
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD
    

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BWWBSV2

) AS

SELECT
    T1.WBSNRLOG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.WBSTPVAL,
    T1.WBSNATCO,
    T1.WBSTPSTP,
    T1.WBSINCMR,
    T1.WBSTOTAT,
    T1.WBSTOTPA,
    T1.WBSSTANS,
    T1.WBSNODEC,
    T1.WSBDECOD,
    T1.WBSFVCSZ,
    T1.SBCCSDBC,
    T3.SBCDSNOR,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T4.T64DESNO,
    T1.WBSCDPER,
    T5.T64DESNO,
    T1.T36CD,
    T6.T36DSNOR,
    T1.T36CD2,
    T7.T36DSNOR,
    T1.T33CD,
    T1.WBSSBCDS
FROM
      FINANCE.BWWBSPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT36PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.T36CD2 = T7.T36CD

         FINANCE.BBT36PT T6

    T1.DIZSTATO,

    T3.VOCDSNOR,
    T3.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CP17RSAT,

    T4.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CP17RSPA,

    T5.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CCPTPCLR,
    T1.CP17RIPR,
    T6.VOCDSNOR,
    T6.VOCDSRID,
    T1.T02CD,
    T7.T02DSNOR,
    T7.T02DSRID,
    T1.CP17RICO,
    T8.VOCDSNOR,
    T8.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CP17CRIC,
    T9.T02DSNOR,
    T9.T02DSRID,
    T1.CP17EMPR,

    T10.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CP17CEMP,
    T11.T02DSNOR,
    T11.T02DSRID,
    T1.CP17EMCO,

    T12.VOCDSRID,
    T1.CP17CEMC,
    T13.T02DSNOR,
    T13.T02DSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.BBCC17PT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T13
     ON  T1.T01CD = T13.T01CD AND
         T1.CP17CEMC = T13.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T12
     ON  T1.T01CD = T12.T01CD AND
         T1.CP17EMCO = T12.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T11
     ON  T1.T01CD = T11.T01CD AND
         T1.CP17CEMP = T11.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN

         T1.CP17EMPR = T10.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN

     ON  T1.T01CD = T9.T01CD AND
         T1.CP17CRIC = T9.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T8
     ON  T1.T01CD = T8.T01CD AND
         T1.CP17RICO = T8.VOCCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT02PT T7
     ON  T1.T01CD = T7.T01CD AND
         T1.T02CD = T7.T02CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35913/tddml/DOC_VEN_TES_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V01
    (
        R_NUM_FAT,
        R_SERIE_NUM_FAT,
        R_LINGUA,
		ID_LINEA_CREDITO,
        STATO,
        COL_MAGAZZINO,
        TIPO_BOLLA,
        STP_BOLLA,
        FAT_SOSPESA,
        TP_DOC_VEN,
        ID_AZIENDA,
        STATO_AVANZAMENTO,
        STP_FATTURA,
        COL_CONTABILITA,
        DATA_DOC,
        DATA_BOLLA,
        ANNO_BOLLA,
        NUMERO_BOLLA,
        DATA_FATTURA,
        ANNO_FAT,
        NUMERO_FATTURA,
        R_CLIENTE_FAT,
        R_CLIENTE,
        R_SEQUENZA_IND,
        R_DEN_ABT,
        RAGIONE_SOC_DEN,
        INDIRIZZO_DEN,
		LOCALITA_DEN,CAP_DEN,R_NAZIONE_DEN,R_PROVINCIA_DEN,
        R_DIVISIONE,
        R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
        R_CAT_CONT_CLI,
        R_VALUTA,
        R_ASSOG_IVA,
        R_AGENTE,
        R_AGENTE_SUB,
        R_COMMESSA,
        R_MOD_PAGAMENTO,
        DATA_INIZIO_PAG,
        SCONTO_FINE_FATT,
        R_MOD_SPEDIZIONE,
        R_MOD_CONSEGNA,
        RAG_BOLLE_FAT,
        FAT_PERIODICA,
        ADB_SPS_INCASSO,
        ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA,
        ID_ANNO_DOC,
        ID_NUMERO_DOC,
        CAU_CONTABILE,
        CODIFICA_SIA,
        R_ABI,
        R_CAB,
        R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
        NUM_CONTO_COR,
        CODICE_CIG,
        CODICE_CUP,
        FATTURA_PA,
        SPLIT_PAYMENT,
        DEST_FATT_PA,
        RIF_AMMINISTR,
		TIPO_BENE_DEP,
        INDIRIZZO_PEC,
        FATTORE_CAMBI,
		RITENUTA_ACC,
		SCN_FINALE_FAT,
		PRC_SCNFIN_FAT,
		TOT_SCN_FIN_FAT,
		TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI,
		R_CAUCONT_OSS_BEN,
		R_CAUCONT_OSS_SRV,
		R_ASSOGG_IVA_OSS, 
		SCORPORO_IVA
    ) AS
SELECT
    C.R_NUM_FAT,
    C.R_SERIE_NUM_FAT,
    D.R_LINGUA,
	D.ID_LINEA_CREDITO,
    D.STATO,
    D.COL_MAGAZZINO,
    D.TIPO_BOLLA,
    D.STP_BOLLA,
    D.FAT_SOSPESA,
    D.TP_DOC_VEN,
    D.ID_AZIENDA,
    D.STATO_AVANZAMENTO,
    D.STP_FATTURA,
    D.COL_CONTABILITA,
    D.DATA_DOC,
    D.DATA_BOLLA,
    D.ANNO_BOLLA,
    D.NUMERO_BOLLA,
    D.DATA_FATTURA,
	D.ANNO_FAT,
	CASE 
		WHEN (V.TIPO_BENE_DEP ='3' OR V.TIPO_BENE_DEP IS NULL)
		THEN D.NUMERO_FATTURA
		ELSE
		V.NUMERO_FATTURA
	END NUMERO_FATTURA,
    D.R_CLIENTE_FAT,
    D.R_CLIENTE,
    D.R_SEQUENZA_IND,
    D.R_DEN_ABT,
    D.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN,
    D.INDIRIZZO_DEN,
	D.LOCALITA_DEN,D.CAP_DEN,D.R_NAZIONE_DEN,D.R_PROVINCIA_DEN,
    D.R_DIVISIONE,
    D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
    D.R_CAT_CONT_CLI,
    D.R_VALUTA,
    D.R_ASSOG_IVA,
    D.R_AGENTE,
    D.R_AGENTE_SUB,
    D.R_COMMESSA,
    D.R_MOD_PAGAMENTO,
    D.DATA_INIZIO_PAG,
    D.SCONTO_FINE_FATT,
    D.R_MOD_SPEDIZIONE,
    D.R_MOD_CONSEGNA,
    D.RAG_BOLLE_FAT,
    D.FAT_PERIODICA,
    D.ADB_SPS_INCASSO,
    D.ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA,
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC,
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC,
    CASE
        WHEN (NOT G.R_CAU_CONTABILE IS NULL)
        THEN G.R_CAU_CONTABILE
        ELSE C.R_CAU_CONTABILE
    END AS CAU_CONTABILE,
    D.CODIFICA_SIA,
    D.R_ABI ,
    D.R_CAB,
    D.R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
    D.NUM_CONTO_COR,
    CM.CODICE_CIG,
    CM.CODICE_CUP,
    D.FATTURA_PA,
    D.SPLIT_PAYMENT,
    D.ID_DESTIN_FAT,
    D.RIF_AMMINISTR,
	CASE 
		WHEN (V.TIPO_BENE_DEP IS NULL)
		THEN '3'
		ELSE
                V.TIPO_BENE_DEP
	END TIPO_BENE_DEP,
    D.INDIRIZZO_PEC,
    D.FATTORE_CAMBI,
	D.RITENUTA_ACC,
	D.SCN_FINALE_FAT,
	D.PRC_SCNFIN_FAT,
	D.TOT_SCN_FIN_FAT,
	C.TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI,
	C.R_CAUCONT_OSS_BEN,
	C.R_CAUCONT_OSS_SRV,
	C.R_ASSOGG_IVA_OSS, 
	C.SCORPORO_IVA
	
FROM
    THIP.DOC_VEN_TES D
JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN C
ON
    C.ID_AZIENDA = D.ID_AZIENDA
AND C.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN = D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN
LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN_CAT G
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = G.ID_AZIENDA1
AND D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN = G.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN
AND D.R_CAT_CONT_CLI = G.ID_CAT_CON_CLI
LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.COMMESSE CM
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = CM.ID_AZIENDA
AND D.R_COMMESSA = CM.ID_COMMESSA
LEFT OUTER JOIN
	THIP.FATVEN_TP_BENE V 
ON 
    D.ID_AZIENDA = V.ID_AZIENDA AND
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC = V.ID_ANNO_DOC AND
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC = V.ID_NUMERO_DOC
WHERE
    D.STATO = 'V'
AND D.STATO_AVANZAMENTO= '2'
AND FAT_SOSPESA = 'N'
AND D.COL_MAGAZZINO > '1'
AND D.TIPO_BOLLA != '2'
AND D.STP_BOLLA > '1'
GRANT ALL ON THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V01 TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36668/tddml/ORD_SRV_LTM_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.ORD_SRV_LTM_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.ORD_SRV_LTM_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.ORD_SRV_LTM_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    M.ID_AZIENDA, 
    M.ID_ANNO_ORD, 
    M.ID_NUMERO_ORD, 
    M.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, 
    M.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE, 
    M.R_ARTICOLO, 
    M.R_VERSIONE, 
    M.R_CONFIGURAZIONE, 
    CASE 
        WHEN A.GES_SALDI_COMMES = 'Y' 
        AND C.AGGIOR_SALDI      = 'Y' 
        THEN M.R_COMMESSA 
        ELSE NULL 
    END 
    R_COMMESSA, 
    M.R_COMMESSA AS R_COMMESSA_ORG, 
    CFG.COD_CONFIG, 
    M.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL, 
    M.R_MAGAZZINO_RFR, 
    M.R_UM_PRM_MAG, 
    M.R_UM_SEC_MAG, 
    M.DATA_PRV_IMPIEGO, 
    M.MOD_PRELIEVO, 
    M.STATO_PRL_MAT, 
    M.STATO, 
    A.R_GRP_PRODOTTO, 
    A.R_CLASSE_MERCLG, 
    A.R_PIANIFICATORE, 
    A.GES_SALDI_COMMES, 
    A.LOTTO_MINIMO, 
    A.LOTTO_MULTIPLO, 
    L.ID_LOTTO, 
    L.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM, 
    L.QTA_RCS_UM_SEC, 
    L.QTA_PRL_UM_PRM, 
    L.QTA_PRL_UM_SEC, 
    L.QTA_SCA_UM_PRM, 
    L.QTA_SCA_UM_SEC, 
    L.QTA_RESA_UM_PRM, 
    L.QTA_RESA_UM_SEC, 
    CASE 
        WHEN STATO_LOTTO = '2' 
        THEN 0 
        WHEN STATO_LOTTO     < '2' 
        AND L.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM > COALESCE(L.QTA_PRL_UM_PRM,0) 
        THEN (L.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM - COALESCE(L.QTA_PRL_UM_PRM,0)) 
        ELSE 0 
    END 
    QTA_RES_UM_PRM, 
    CASE 
        WHEN STATO_LOTTO = '2' 
        THEN 0 
        WHEN STATO_LOTTO                 < '2' 
        AND COALESCE(L.QTA_RCS_UM_SEC,0) > COALESCE(L.QTA_PRL_UM_SEC,0) 
        THEN (COALESCE(L.QTA_RCS_UM_SEC,0) - COALESCE(L.QTA_PRL_UM_SEC,0)) 
        ELSE 0 
    END 
    QTA_RES_UM_SEC, 
    L.STATO_LOTTO 
FROM 
    THIP.ORD_SRV_MAT M 
INNER JOIN 
    THIP.ARTICOLI A 
    ON 
    M.ID_AZIENDA     = A.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND M.R_ARTICOLO = A.ID_ARTICOLO 
INNER JOIN 
    THIP.ORD_SRV_LTM L 
    ON 
    M.ID_AZIENDA            = L.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND M.ID_ANNO_ORD       = L.ID_ANNO_ORD 
    AND M.ID_NUMERO_ORD     = L.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
    AND M.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA  = L.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA 
    AND M.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE = L.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE 
LEFT OUTER JOIN 
    THIP.COMMESSE C 
    ON 
    M.ID_AZIENDA     = C.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND M.R_COMMESSA = C.ID_COMMESSA 
LEFT OUTER JOIN 
    THIP.CONFIGURAZIONI CFG 
    ON 
    M.ID_AZIENDA           = CFG.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND M.R_CONFIGURAZIONE = CFG.ID_CONFIG

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36769/primrose/script/04VistaPAFW300X.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.PAFW300X 
CREATE VIEW THIP.PAFW300X 
(
	PW_KEYPRGINVIO, 
	PW_KEYHEADERFATT, 
	PW_KEYBODYFATT, 
	PW_TIPODOC, 
	PW_TIPONUM, 
	PW_NUMERO, 
	PW_DATA, 
	PW_CODSDI, 
	PW_CLIENTE, 
	PW_RAGSOC, 
	PW_PAESE, 
	PW_CODICE, 
	PW_CFISCA, 
	PW_DENOM, 
	PW_NOME, 
	PW_COGN, 
	PW_CDEST, 
	PW_IMPO, 
	PW_FNOT, 
	PW_CXML,
        PW_CXMLP,
        PW_UPAG,
        PW_GESTIONE	
)
AS SELECT 
	P1_KEYPRGINVIO, 
	P1_KEYHEADERFATT, 
	P1_KEYBODYFATT, 
	P7_TIPODOC, 
	' ', 
	P7_NUMERO, 
	P7_DATA, 
	CASE WHEN ID_SDI IS NOT NULL THEN STR(ID_SDI) WHEN PW_CODSDI IS NOT NULL THEN PW_CODSDI ELSE ' ' END, 
	SUBSTRING(P1_KEYHEADERFATT, 4, 8), 
	' ',  
	P4_FISCIVAPAESE, 
	P4_FISCIVACOD, 
	P4_CODFISC, 
	P4_ANADENOM, 
	P4_ANANOME, 
	P4_ANACOGNOME, 
	P1_CODDEST, 
	0, 
	' ', 
	CASE WHEN NOME_FILE_XML IS NOT NULL THEN NOME_FILE_XML WHEN PW_CXML IS NOT NULL THEN PW_CXML ELSE RTRIM(P1_TRASMITTPAESE) + RTRIM(P1_TRASMITTCOD) + '_'  + RTRIM(P1_KEYPRGINVIO) + '.xml' END,
	' ', 
	COALESCE(DATA_INVIO_SDI, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)), 
	P1_GESTIONE
FROM THIP.PAF0100F A
INNER JOIN THIP.PAF0400F B ON 
	B.P4_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	B.P4_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND  
	B.P4_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
INNER JOIN THIP.PAF0700F C ON 
	C.P7_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	C.P7_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND  
	C.P7_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATVEN_INVII_SDI D ON 
	D.R_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	D.R_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	D.R_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAFW300F E ON 
	E.PW_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	E.PW_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	E.PW_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
WHERE P1_GESTIONE='N' 
UNION SELECT 
	MAX(P1_KEYPRGINVIO), 
	P1_KEYHEADERFATT, 
	P1_KEYBODYFATT, 
	MAX(P7_TIPODOC), 
	' ', 
	MAX(P7_NUMERO), 
	MAX(P7_DATA), 
	MAX(CASE WHEN ID_SDI IS NOT NULL THEN STR(ID_SDI) WHEN PW_CODSDI IS NOT NULL THEN PW_CODSDI ELSE ' ' END), 
	SUBSTRING(P1_KEYHEADERFATT, 4, 8), 
	' ',  
	MAX(P4_FISCIVAPAESE), 
	MAX(P4_FISCIVACOD), 
	MAX(P4_CODFISC), 
	MAX(P4_ANADENOM), 
	MAX(P4_ANANOME), 
	MAX(P4_ANACOGNOME), 
	MAX(P1_CODDEST), 
	0, 
	'0', 
	MAX(CASE WHEN NOME_FILE_XML IS NOT NULL THEN NOME_FILE_XML WHEN PW_CXML IS NOT NULL THEN PW_CXML ELSE RTRIM(P1_TRASMITTPAESE) + RTRIM(P1_TRASMITTCOD) + '_'  + RTRIM(P1_KEYPRGINVIO) + '.xml' END),
	' ', 
	MAX(COALESCE(DATA_INVIO_SDI, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120))), 
	MAX(P1_GESTIONE)
FROM THIP.PAF0100F A
INNER JOIN THIP.PAF0400F B ON 
	B.P4_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	B.P4_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	B.P4_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT 
INNER JOIN THIP.PAF0700F C ON 
	C.P7_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	C.P7_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	C.P7_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATVEN_INVII_SDI D ON 
	D.R_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	D.R_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	D.R_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAFW300F E ON 
	E.PW_KEYPRGINVIO=A.P1_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
	E.PW_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
	E.PW_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT
WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM THIP.PAF0100F Z 
		  WHERE Z.P1_KEYHEADERFATT=A.P1_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
		  Z.P1_KEYBODYFATT=A.P1_KEYBODYFATT AND 
		  Z.P1_GESTIONE='N') 
GROUP BY P1_KEYHEADERFATT, P1_KEYBODYFATT

E' stata applicata la fix 36769

#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BWWMC4PT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BWWMC4PT
(
   WMCNRLOG NUMERIC(9,0) NOT NULL,
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T96CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   T01CDFIL CHAR(3),
   T96FIL CHAR(8),
   T97FIL CHAR(8),
   T91FIL NUMERIC(7,0),
   T91VLCB1 CHAR(60),
   T91VLCB2 CHAR(60),
   T91VLCB3 CHAR(60),
   T91VLCB4 CHAR(60)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BWWMC4PT TO PUBLIC

DROP VIEW THIP.DOCUMENTI_SSD_V02
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOCUMENTI_SSD_V02' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE
	VIEW THIP.DOCUMENTI_SSD_V02 AS

SELECT
A.DOC_ID,
A.STATUS,
A.DELIVERY_INI_DATE,
A.DELIVERY_FIN_DATE,
A.TIMESTAMP_CRZ,
A.R_UTENTE_CRZ,
A.DOC_TYPE_ID,
B.R_AZIENDA,
B.R_CLIENTE,
B.R_FORNITORE,
B.R_AGENTE,
B.R_ARTICOLO,
B.R_COMMESSA,
B.R_ATTIVITA,
B.R_TIPO_DOC_DGT,
B.R_BENE,
B.R_DIPENDENTE

FROM THERA.SSD_DOCUMENT A, THIP.DOCUMENTI_SSD B
WHERE 
A.DOC_ID = B.DOC_ID
GRANT ALL ON THIP.DOCUMENTI_SSD_V02 TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THIP.STORICO_CMM_DET
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_PROGR_STORIC INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_COMPON_COSTO CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DETTAGLIO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   ID_COMMESSA CHAR(10),
   COSTO_LIVELLO DECIMAL(19,6),
   COSTO_LIVELLI_INF DECIMAL(19,6),
   COSTO_TOTALE DECIMAL(19,6),
   TEMPO_LIVELLO DECIMAL(7,3),
   TEMPO_LIVELLI_INF DECIMAL(7,3),
   TEMPO_TOTALE DECIMAL(7,3),
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX STORIC_CMM_DET_I01 ON THIP.STORICO_CMM_DET (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_PROGR_STORIC ASC, ID_COMPON_COSTO ASC, TIPO_DETTAGLIO ASC)

DROP VIEW FINANCE.THMOTVL_V1
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THMOTVL_V1 AS 
		SELECT 
			T2.T01CD,T2.T09CD, T1.TACQANFI, T1.TACQNRFT, T1.TRAIIVVE, T2.MOVAAPAR TACQANPC,
			T2.MOVNUREG,T2.MOVTCLFO, T2.MOVSTATO, T2.DIZUTCRE, T2.DIZDTCRE, T2.DIZHHCRE, T2.DIZUTAGG, 
			T2.DIZDTAGG, T2.DIZHHAGG, T2.MOVTPVAL, T2.T04CD, T2.T15CD, T2.MOVDTRCO, 	
			T2.MOVDTCOM,T2.MOVDTIVA, T2.MOVDTDOC, T2.MOVDTOPE, T2.MOVDTCOA,	T2.MOVDTSPA,T2.MOVNRPAR, 
			T2.T29CD, T2.MOVCAMBVP, T2.MOVTICAU, T2.MOVDSCAU, T2.MOVDSAGG, T2.MOVCAMBVS, T2.T02CD, T2.T02DSNOR, 
			T2.T02DSRID, T2.T22CD, T2.T22DSNOR, T2.T22DSRID, T2.T36CD, T2.T30CD, COALESCE(T1.NUMDOC, T2.MOVNDORI) AS MOVNDORI, T2.MOVNUPRA, 
			T2.T40CD,T2.CLICD, T2.CLIDSRID, T2.CLIRASOC, T2.FORCD, T2.FORRASOC, T2.FORDSRID, T2.VOCCD, 	
			T2.VOCDSNOR,T2.VOCDSRID, T2.T16CD, T2.T23CD, T2.T17CD, T2.T07CD, T2.MOVNPIVA,T2.MOVIVADF, 
			T2.FORSOFAC, T2.MOVVPDIM, T2.MOVVSDIM, T2.MOVVEDIM, T2.MOVINUSO,T2.MOVDTVAL, T2.FOBNPROG, T2.CLBNPROG, MOVABCAB, 
			T2.T39CD, T2.T38CDABI, T2.T38CDCAB, T2.MOVNCCOR, T2.MOVCCIN, T2.MOVBIC, T2.MOVIBAN, T2.T97CD, 
			CASE WHEN T1.TACQANFI IS NOT NULL THEN T1.TACQANFI ELSE T2.ANNO_DOC END AS ANNO_DOC, 
			CASE WHEN T1.TACQNRFT IS NOT NULL THEN T1.TACQNRFT ELSE T2.NUM_DOC_FORM END AS NUM_DOC_FORM, 
			T2.MOVSTRREG, 
                	COALESCE(TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI, ' ') AS TPDOCSDI
		FROM FINANCE.THMOTVL T2 
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.THACQVL T1 ON 
			T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND 
			T1.T09CD = T2.T09CD AND 
			T1.TRANREGG = T2.MOVNUREG
                LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMFEPT T3 ON 
			T3.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND 
			T3.T09CD = T2.T09CD AND 
			T3.MOVNUREG = T2.MOVNUREG
                LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T4 ON 
			T4.KEYPRGINVIO = T3.KEYINVIO AND 
			T4.KEYHEADERFATT = T3.KEY1FATT AND 
			T4.KEYBODYFATT = T3.KEY2FATT

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36950/tddml/CREATE_VIEW_GROUPAUTHORITHIES.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THERA.GROUP_AUTHORITIES_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THERA.GROUP_AUTHORITIES_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THERA.GROUP_AUTHORITIES_V01 (GROUP_ID, ENTITY_ID, TASK_ID) AS
		WITH EXPANDED (GROUP_ID, ENTITY_ID, TASK_ID) AS
			(SELECT s.GROUP_ID, COALESCE(s.ENTITY_ID, pf.ENTITY_ID) AS ENTITY_ID, s.TASK_ID FROM
				(SELECT * FROM THERA.AUTHORITY WHERE GROUP_ID IS NOT NULL) AS s
				LEFT JOIN 
				THERA.PARENT_FOLDERS pf ON pf.PARENT_FOLDER_ID = s.FOLDER_ID
			)
		SELECT e.GROUP_ID, t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID FROM 
			EXPANDED e 
			JOIN 
			(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID IS NULL)
		GROUP BY t.ENTITY_ID, e.GROUP_ID, t.TASK_ID
		UNION
		SELECT e.GROUP_ID, t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID FROM 
			EXPANDED e 
			JOIN 
			(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID = t.TASK_ID)
		GROUP BY t.ENTITY_ID, e.GROUP_ID, t.TASK_ID

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36950/tddml/CREATE_VIEW_USERAUTHORITIES.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THERA.USER_AUTHORITIES_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THERA.USER_AUTHORITIES_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THERA.USER_AUTHORITIES_V01 AS
			WITH EXPANDED (USER_ID, ENTITY_ID, TASK_ID, GROUP_ID, FROM_USER) AS
				(SELECT s.USER_ID, COALESCE(s.ENTITY_ID, pf.ENTITY_ID) AS ENTITY_ID, s.TASK_ID, s.GROUP_ID,  s.FROM_USER FROM
					(SELECT COALESCE (a.USER_ID , ug.USER_ID) AS USER_ID, a.FOLDER_ID, a.ENTITY_ID, a.TASK_ID, a.GROUP_ID, a.USER_ID AS FROM_USER FROM 
						THERA.AUTHORITY a 
						LEFT JOIN 
						THERA.USER_GROUP ug ON a.GROUP_ID = ug.GROUP_ID
					) AS s
					LEFT JOIN 
					THERA.PARENT_FOLDERS pf ON pf.PARENT_FOLDER_ID = s.FOLDER_ID
				WHERE USER_ID IS NOT NULL)
			SELECT q.USER_ID, q.ENTITY_ID, q.TASK_ID, STRING_AGG(q.GROUP_ID, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY q.GROUP_ID) AS GROUPS, CASE WHEN COUNT(q.FROM_USER) > 0
				   THEN 'Y' 
				   ELSE 'N'
			  END AS FROM_USER FROM
				(SELECT DISTINCT f.ENTITY_ID, f.TASK_ID, f.GROUP_ID, f.USER_ID, f.FROM_USER FROM
					(SELECT t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID, e.GROUP_ID, e.USER_ID, e.FROM_USER FROM 
						EXPANDED e 
						JOIN 
						(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID IS NULL)
					UNION
					SELECT t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID, e.GROUP_ID, e.USER_ID, e.FROM_USER FROM 
						EXPANDED e 
						JOIN 
						(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID = t.TASK_ID)
					) AS f
				) AS q
			GROUP BY ENTITY_ID, USER_ID, TASK_ID
#WARNING#
Sintassi non corretta in prossimità di '('.


CREATE VIEW THERA.USER_AUTHORITIES_V01 AS
			WITH EXPANDED (USER_ID, ENTITY_ID, TASK_ID, ENTITY_FROM_FOLDER, GROUP_ID, FROM_USER) AS
				(SELECT s.USER_ID, s.ENTITY_ID, s.TASK_ID, pf.ENTITY_ID, s.GROUP_ID, s.FROM_USER FROM
					(SELECT COALESCE (a.USER_ID , ug.USER_ID) AS USER_ID, a.FOLDER_ID, a.ENTITY_ID, a.TASK_ID, a.GROUP_ID, a.USER_ID AS FROM_USER FROM 
						THERA.AUTHORITY a 
						LEFT JOIN 
						THERA.USER_GROUP ug ON a.GROUP_ID = ug.GROUP_ID
					) AS s
					LEFT JOIN 
					THERA.PARENT_FOLDERS pf ON pf.PARENT_FOLDER_ID = s.FOLDER_ID
				WHERE USER_ID IS NOT NULL)
			SELECT q.USER_ID, q.ENTITY_ID, q.TASK_ID,GROUPS = STUFF((SELECT ', ' + z.GRUPPO FROM(
				SELECT GROUP_ID AS GRUPPO FROM EXPANDED e WHERE e.ENTITY_ID = q.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID IS NULL AND e.USER_ID = q.USER_ID
				UNION
				SELECT GROUP_ID AS GRUPPO FROM EXPANDED e WHERE e.ENTITY_ID = q.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID = q.TASK_ID AND e.USER_ID = q.USER_ID
				UNION 
				SELECT GROUP_ID AS GRUPPO FROM EXPANDED e WHERE e.ENTITY_FROM_FOLDER = q.ENTITY_ID AND e.USER_ID = q.USER_ID) AS z FOR XML PATH('')), 1, 2, ''), 
				CASE WHEN COUNT(q.FROM_USER) > 0
				   THEN 'Y' 
				   ELSE 'N'
			  END AS FROM_USER  FROM
				(SELECT DISTINCT f.ENTITY_ID, f.TASK_ID, f.GROUP_ID, f.USER_ID, f.FROM_USER FROM
					(SELECT t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID, e.GROUP_ID, e.USER_ID, e.FROM_USER FROM 
						EXPANDED e 
						JOIN 
						(SELECT TASK_ID , ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_FROM_FOLDER
					UNION 
					SELECT t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID, e.GROUP_ID, e.USER_ID, e.FROM_USER FROM 
						EXPANDED e 
						JOIN 
						(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID IS NULL)
					UNION
					SELECT t.ENTITY_ID, t.TASK_ID, e.GROUP_ID, e.USER_ID, e.FROM_USER FROM 
						EXPANDED e 
						JOIN 
						(SELECT TASK_ID, ENTITY_ID FROM THERA.TASK) AS t ON (t.ENTITY_ID = e.ENTITY_ID AND e.TASK_ID = t.TASK_ID)
					) AS f
				) AS q
			GROUP BY ENTITY_ID, USER_ID, TASK_ID

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36915/tddml/CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI.TDDML.
CREATE TABLE THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_CLIENTE CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   ID_RAPPRES_FISC NUMERIC(3) NOT NULL,
   R_FORNITORE CHAR(8),
   R_NAZIONE CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   PARTITA_IVA CHAR(28) NOT NULL,
   DENOMINAZIONE VARCHAR(80),
   COGNOME VARCHAR(60),
   NOME VARCHAR(60),
   DEFAULT_RAPPR CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N'
)
********** #WARNING# **********
Tablespace non specificato per la tabella, usato quello di default.
CREATE TABLE THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_CLIENTE CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   ID_RAPPRES_FISC NUMERIC(3) NOT NULL,
   R_FORNITORE CHAR(8),
   R_NAZIONE CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   PARTITA_IVA CHAR(28) NOT NULL,
   DENOMINAZIONE VARCHAR(80),
   COGNOME VARCHAR(60),
   NOME VARCHAR(60),
   DEFAULT_RAPPR CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N'
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CLI_R_FIS_I01 ON THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_CLIENTE ASC, ID_RAPPRES_FISC ASC)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CLI_R_FIS_I02 ON THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_CLIENTE ASC, R_NAZIONE ASC, PARTITA_IVA ASC, DENOMINAZIONE ASC, COGNOME ASC, NOME ASC)

GRANT ALL ON THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36915/tddml/CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI_V01
    (
		ID_AZIENDA,
		ID_CLIENTE,
		ID_RAPPRES_FISC,
		R_FORNITORE, 
		R_NAZIONE, 
		PARTITA_IVA, 
		DENOMINAZIONE, 
		COGNOME, 
		NOME, 
		DEFAULT_RAPPR,
		RAGIONE_SOCIALE
    ) AS
SELECT
	ID_AZIENDA,
	ID_CLIENTE,
	ID_RAPPRES_FISC,
	R_FORNITORE,
	R_NAZIONE,
	PARTITA_IVA,
	DENOMINAZIONE,
	COGNOME,
	NOME,
	DEFAULT_RAPPR,
	CASE 
		WHEN (CR.DENOMINAZIONE IS NULL)
		THEN  CR.COGNOME + ' ' + CR.NOME
		ELSE
             CR.DENOMINAZIONE
	END AS RAGIONE_SOCIALE
	
FROM
    THIP.CLI_RAPPR_FISCALI CR

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36915/tddml/DOC_VEN_TES_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOC_VEN_TES_V01
    (
        R_NUM_FAT,
        R_SERIE_NUM_FAT,
        R_LINGUA,
		ID_LINEA_CREDITO,
        STATO,
        COL_MAGAZZINO,
        TIPO_BOLLA,
        STP_BOLLA,
        FAT_SOSPESA,
        TP_DOC_VEN,
        ID_AZIENDA,
        STATO_AVANZAMENTO,
        STP_FATTURA,
        COL_CONTABILITA,
        DATA_DOC,
        DATA_BOLLA,
        ANNO_BOLLA,
        NUMERO_BOLLA,
        DATA_FATTURA,
        ANNO_FAT,
        NUMERO_FATTURA,
        R_CLIENTE_FAT,
        R_CLIENTE,
        R_SEQUENZA_IND,
        R_DEN_ABT,
        RAGIONE_SOC_DEN,
        INDIRIZZO_DEN,
		LOCALITA_DEN,CAP_DEN,R_NAZIONE_DEN,R_PROVINCIA_DEN,
        R_DIVISIONE,
        R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
        R_CAT_CONT_CLI,
        R_VALUTA,
        R_ASSOG_IVA,
        R_AGENTE,
        R_AGENTE_SUB,
        R_COMMESSA,
        R_MOD_PAGAMENTO,
        DATA_INIZIO_PAG,
        SCONTO_FINE_FATT,
        R_MOD_SPEDIZIONE,
        R_MOD_CONSEGNA,
        RAG_BOLLE_FAT,
        FAT_PERIODICA,
        ADB_SPS_INCASSO,
        ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA,
        ID_ANNO_DOC,
        ID_NUMERO_DOC,
        CAU_CONTABILE,
        CODIFICA_SIA,
        R_ABI,
        R_CAB,
        R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
        NUM_CONTO_COR,
        CODICE_CIG,
        CODICE_CUP,
        FATTURA_PA,
        SPLIT_PAYMENT,
        DEST_FATT_PA,
        RIF_AMMINISTR,
		TIPO_BENE_DEP,
        INDIRIZZO_PEC,
        FATTORE_CAMBI,
		RITENUTA_ACC,
		SCN_FINALE_FAT,
		PRC_SCNFIN_FAT,
		TOT_SCN_FIN_FAT,
		TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI,
		R_CAUCONT_OSS_BEN,
		R_CAUCONT_OSS_SRV,
		R_ASSOGG_IVA_OSS, 
		SCORPORO_IVA,
		R_RAPPRES_FISC
    ) AS
SELECT
    C.R_NUM_FAT,
    C.R_SERIE_NUM_FAT,
    D.R_LINGUA,
	D.ID_LINEA_CREDITO,
    D.STATO,
    D.COL_MAGAZZINO,
    D.TIPO_BOLLA,
    D.STP_BOLLA,
    D.FAT_SOSPESA,
    D.TP_DOC_VEN,
    D.ID_AZIENDA,
    D.STATO_AVANZAMENTO,
    D.STP_FATTURA,
    D.COL_CONTABILITA,
    D.DATA_DOC,
    D.DATA_BOLLA,
    D.ANNO_BOLLA,
    D.NUMERO_BOLLA,
    D.DATA_FATTURA,
	D.ANNO_FAT,
	CASE 
		WHEN (V.TIPO_BENE_DEP ='3' OR V.TIPO_BENE_DEP IS NULL)
		THEN D.NUMERO_FATTURA
		ELSE
		V.NUMERO_FATTURA
	END NUMERO_FATTURA,
    D.R_CLIENTE_FAT,
    D.R_CLIENTE,
    D.R_SEQUENZA_IND,
    D.R_DEN_ABT,
    D.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN,
    D.INDIRIZZO_DEN,
	D.LOCALITA_DEN,D.CAP_DEN,D.R_NAZIONE_DEN,D.R_PROVINCIA_DEN,
    D.R_DIVISIONE,
    D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN,
    D.R_CAT_CONT_CLI,
    D.R_VALUTA,
    D.R_ASSOG_IVA,
    D.R_AGENTE,
    D.R_AGENTE_SUB,
    D.R_COMMESSA,
    D.R_MOD_PAGAMENTO,
    D.DATA_INIZIO_PAG,
    D.SCONTO_FINE_FATT,
    D.R_MOD_SPEDIZIONE,
    D.R_MOD_CONSEGNA,
    D.RAG_BOLLE_FAT,
    D.FAT_PERIODICA,
    D.ADB_SPS_INCASSO,
    D.ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA,
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC,
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC,
    CASE
        WHEN (NOT G.R_CAU_CONTABILE IS NULL)
        THEN G.R_CAU_CONTABILE
        ELSE C.R_CAU_CONTABILE
    END AS CAU_CONTABILE,
    D.CODIFICA_SIA,
    D.R_ABI ,
    D.R_CAB,
    D.R_BANCA_NON_ABI,
    D.NUM_CONTO_COR,
    CM.CODICE_CIG,
    CM.CODICE_CUP,
    D.FATTURA_PA,
    D.SPLIT_PAYMENT,
    D.ID_DESTIN_FAT,
    D.RIF_AMMINISTR,
	CASE 
		WHEN (V.TIPO_BENE_DEP IS NULL)
		THEN '3'
		ELSE
                V.TIPO_BENE_DEP
	END TIPO_BENE_DEP,
    D.INDIRIZZO_PEC,
    D.FATTORE_CAMBI,
	D.RITENUTA_ACC,
	D.SCN_FINALE_FAT,
	D.PRC_SCNFIN_FAT,
	D.TOT_SCN_FIN_FAT,
	C.TIPO_DOCUMENTO_SDI,
	C.R_CAUCONT_OSS_BEN,
	C.R_CAUCONT_OSS_SRV,
	C.R_ASSOGG_IVA_OSS, 
	C.SCORPORO_IVA,
	D.R_RAPPRES_FISC
	
FROM
    THIP.DOC_VEN_TES D
JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN C
ON
    C.ID_AZIENDA = D.ID_AZIENDA
AND C.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN = D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN
LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN_CAT G
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = G.ID_AZIENDA1
AND D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN = G.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN
AND D.R_CAT_CONT_CLI = G.ID_CAT_CON_CLI
LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.COMMESSE CM
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = CM.ID_AZIENDA
AND D.R_COMMESSA = CM.ID_COMMESSA
LEFT OUTER JOIN
	THIP.FATVEN_TP_BENE V 
ON 
    D.ID_AZIENDA = V.ID_AZIENDA AND
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC = V.ID_ANNO_DOC AND
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC = V.ID_NUMERO_DOC
WHERE
    D.STATO = 'V'
AND D.STATO_AVANZAMENTO= '2'
AND FAT_SOSPESA = 'N'
AND D.COL_MAGAZZINO > '1'
AND D.TIPO_BOLLA != '2'
AND D.STP_BOLLA > '1'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36963/tddml/DOC_DGT_CORRENTE_VALIDO.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_CORRENTE_VALIDO
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOC_DGT_CORRENTE_VALIDO' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_CORRENTE_VALIDO 
                AS 
                     SELECT * FROM THIP.DOC_DGT  
                     WHERE STATO = 'V' AND (TIPO_VERSIONE =  '-'  OR TIPO_VERSIONE =  '1' )

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36963/tddml/DOC_DGT_PATH_CALCOLO.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_PATH_CALCOLO
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOC_DGT_PATH_CALCOLO' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_PATH_CALCOLO 
                AS 
                   SELECT  DGTVAL.*,
					CASE
 	                    WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT,LEN(PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT),1) != '\'   THEN PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT + '\' 
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT,LEN(PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT),1)  = '\' THEN PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT
						ELSE null
						END
						AS PATH_ROOT,
					CASE
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT,LEN(TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT),1) != '\'  THEN TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT + '\' 
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT,LEN(TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT),1)  = '\'  THEN TPDGT.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT 
						ELSE  NULL
						END
						AS PATH_TP_DOC_DGT,
					CASE
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA,LEN(DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA),1) != '\'  THEN DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA + '\' 
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA IS NOT NULL AND SUBSTRING(DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA,LEN(DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA),1) = '\' THEN DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA
						ELSE  NULL
						END
						AS PATH_SOTTOCARTELLA,
					CASE
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA IS NOT NULL THEN FORMAT(DGTOGG.ID_DOCUMENTO_DGT,'000000000000') + '.' + FORMAT(DGTOGG.ID_VERSIONE,'0000') + '.' + FORMAT(DGTOGG.PROGRESSIVO,'0000')
						ELSE NULL
						END
						AS NOMEFILE_FS,
					CASE
						WHEN PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT ='1' AND DGTOGG.NOME_CARTELLA IS NOT NULL AND CHARINDEX ('.', DGTOGG.FILENAME)>0 THEN REVERSE(SUBSTRING(REVERSE(DGTOGG.FILENAME), 1, CHARINDEX('.', REVERSE(DGTOGG.FILENAME))))
						ELSE NULL
						END
						AS ESTENSIONE
                    FROM  THIP.DOC_DGT_CORRENTE_VALIDO DGTVAL
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PSN_DATI_GEN PSNGEN ON PSNGEN.ID_AZIENDA = DGTVAL.ID_AZIENDA 
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.TP_DOC_DGT TPDGT ON TPDGT.ID_AZIENDA = DGTVAL.ID_AZIENDA  AND  TPDGT.ID_TIPO_DOC_DGT = DGTVAL.R_TIPO_DOC_DGT 
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.DOC_DGT_OGG DGTOGG ON DGTOGG.ID_AZIENDA = DGTVAL.ID_AZIENDA AND DGTVAL.ID_DOCUMENTO_DGT = DGTOGG.ID_DOCUMENTO_DGT AND DGTVAL.ID_VERSIONE = DGTOGG.ID_VERSIONE

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36963/tddml/DOC_DGT_ALLEGATI.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_ALLEGATI
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOC_DGT_ALLEGATI' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOC_DGT_ALLEGATI
                AS 
                    SELECT DGTCALCOLO.* , PSNGEN.MEM_DOC_DGT, PSNGEN.PCS_MEM_DOC_DGT,
						CASE
							WHEN DGTCALCOLO.PATH_ROOT IS NOT NULL AND DGTCALCOLO.PATH_TP_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND DGTCALCOLO.PATH_SOTTOCARTELLA IS NOT NULL AND DGTCALCOLO.NOMEFILE_FS IS NOT NULL 
							THEN DGTCALCOLO.PATH_ROOT + 'GD\' + DGTCALCOLO.PATH_TP_DOC_DGT + DGTCALCOLO.PATH_SOTTOCARTELLA + DGTCALCOLO.NOMEFILE_FS + DGTCALCOLO.ESTENSIONE
							ELSE NULL
							END
						AS PATH_COMPLETO,
						CASE
							WHEN DGTCALCOLO.PATH_TP_DOC_DGT IS NOT NULL AND DGTCALCOLO.PATH_SOTTOCARTELLA IS NOT NULL AND DGTCALCOLO.NOMEFILE_FS  IS NOT NULL
							THEN 'GD\' + DGTCALCOLO.PATH_TP_DOC_DGT +  DGTCALCOLO.PATH_SOTTOCARTELLA + DGTCALCOLO.NOMEFILE_FS + DGTCALCOLO.ESTENSIONE
							ELSE NULL
							END
						AS PATH_COMPLETO_NO_ROOT
                    FROM  THIP.DOC_DGT_PATH_CALCOLO DGTCALCOLO
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PSN_DATI_GEN PSNGEN ON PSNGEN.ID_AZIENDA = DGTCALCOLO.ID_AZIENDA 
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.TP_DOC_DGT TPDGT ON TPDGT.ID_AZIENDA = DGTCALCOLO.ID_AZIENDA  AND  TPDGT.ID_TIPO_DOC_DGT = DGTCALCOLO.R_TIPO_DOC_DGT 
                    LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.DOC_DGT_OGG DGTOGG ON DGTOGG.ID_AZIENDA = DGTCALCOLO.ID_AZIENDA AND DGTCALCOLO.ID_DOCUMENTO_DGT = DGTOGG.ID_DOCUMENTO_DGT AND DGTCALCOLO.ID_VERSIONE = DGTOGG.ID_VERSIONE 
					WHERE DGTOGG.FILENAME IS NOT NULL

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36401/tddml/GRP_CNT_SPC_CA_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.GRP_CNT_SPC_CA_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.GRP_CNT_SPC_CA_V01 AS
		SELECT GRP.ID_AZIENDA, GRP.ID_INTERNO, GRP.R_CDC_DARE, CCD.DESCRIZIONE AS DESC_CDC_DARE, 
		GRP.R_CDC_AVERE, CCA.DESCRIZIONE AS DESC_CDC_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VDS_DARE,  VSD.GPV0DSNO AS DESC_VDS_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VDS_AVERE, VSA.GPV0DSNO AS DESC_VDS_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_CMM_DARE, CMD.DESCRIZIONE AS DESC_CMA_DARE, 
		GRP.R_CMM_AVERE, CMA.DESCRIZIONE AS DESC_CMD_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE4_DARE, VC4D.GPS1DSNO AS DESC_VC4D_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE4_AVERE, VC4A.GPS1DSNO AS DESC_VC4A_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE5_DARE, VC5D.GPS2DSNO AS DESC_VC5D_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE5_AVERE, VC5A.GPS2DSNO AS DESC_VC5A_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE6_DARE, VC6D.GPS3DSNO AS DESC_VC6D_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE6_AVERE, VC6A.GPS3DSNO AS DESC_VC6A_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE7_DARE,  VC7D.GPS4DSNO AS DESC_VC7D_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE7_AVERE, VC7A.GPS4DSNO AS DESC_VC7A_AVERE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE8_DARE,  VC8D.GPS5DSNO AS DESC_VC8D_DARE, 
		GRP.R_VOCE8_AVERE, VC8A.GPS5DSNO AS DESC_VC8A_AVERE

		FROM THIP.GRP_CNT_SPC_CA GRP
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CENTRI_COSTO CCD ON CCD.ID_AZIENDA = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND CCD.ID_CENTRO_COSTO = GRP.R_CDC_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CENTRI_COSTO CCA ON CCA.ID_AZIENDA = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND CCA.ID_CENTRO_COSTO = GRP.R_CDC_AVERE

      		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPV0PT_V01 VSD ON VSD.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VSD.GPV0CD = GRP.R_VDS_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPV0PT_V01 VSA ON VSA.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VSA.GPV0CD = GRP.R_VDS_AVERE

       		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.COMMESSE CMD ON CMD.ID_AZIENDA = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND CMD.ID_COMMESSA = GRP.R_CMM_DARE
      		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.COMMESSE CMA ON CMA.ID_AZIENDA = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND CMA.ID_COMMESSA = GRP.R_CMM_AVERE

        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS1PT_V01 VC4D ON VC4D.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC4D.GPS1CD  = GRP.R_VOCE4_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS1PT_V01 VC4A ON VC4A.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC4A.GPS1CD = GRP.R_VOCE4_AVERE

        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS2PT_V01 VC5D ON VC5D.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC5D.GPS2CD = GRP.R_VOCE5_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS2PT_V01 VC5A ON VC5A.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC5A.GPS2CD = GRP.R_VOCE5_AVERE

        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS3PT_V01 VC6D ON VC6D.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC6D.GPS3CD = GRP.R_VOCE6_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS3PT_V01 VC6A ON VC6A.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC6A.GPS3CD = GRP.R_VOCE6_AVERE

        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS4PT_V01 VC7D ON VC7D.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC7D.GPS4CD = GRP.R_VOCE7_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS4PT_V01 VC7A ON VC7A.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC7A.GPS4CD = GRP.R_VOCE7_AVERE

        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS5PT_V01 VC8D ON VC8D.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC8D.GPS5CD = GRP.R_VOCE8_DARE
        	LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.GPS5PT_V01 VC8A ON VC8A.T01CD = GRP.ID_AZIENDA AND VC8A.GPS5CD = GRP.R_VOCE8_AVERE

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36401/sql/ARTICOLO.SQL.

UPDATE  THERA.CLASSAD_NLS SET  NLS_COLUMN_TITLE ='Dati contabili - Desc. Centro Costo Dare' WHERE CLASS_NAME ='Articolo' AND  ATTRIBUTE_NAME ='DescCentroCostoDare'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37145/tddml/RUBRICHE_MANSIONI_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.RUBRICHE_MANSIONI_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.RUBRICHE_MANSIONI_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.RUBRICHE_MANSIONI_V01 AS 
SELECT DISTINCT THIP.MANSIONI_EXT.ID_MANSIONE, THIP.MANSIONI_EXT.DESCRIZIONE, FINANCE.BBANRPT.ANACD, FINANCE.BBANRPT.ANRCD
FROM THIP.MANSIONI_EXT JOIN THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT ON THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT.R_MANSIONE = THIP.MANSIONI_EXT.ID_MANSIONE 
	INNER JOIN FINANCE.BBANRPT ON THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT.ID_ANAGRAFICO = FINANCE.BBANRPT.ANACD AND THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB = FINANCE.BBANRPT.ANRCD

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37291/tddml/IOF_ORDINI.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.IOF_ORDINI
CREATE VIEW
				THIP.IOF_ORDINI
				(
				ID_AZIENDA, ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, ID_PROGRESSIVO_T, GRUPPO, TIPO_OPERAZIONE_T, STATO_PRC_T, TIMESTAMP_PRC_T, TP_ORDINE,
				ID_ORDINE, ID_MAGAZZINO, ID_ARTICOLO, ID_VERSIONE, ID_CONFIGURAZIONE, ID_COMMESSA, ID_CLIENTE, DESCRIZIONE_T,
				DATA_CONSEGNA, QUANTITA, UM_QUANTITA, STATO_ORDINE,
				ID_PROGRESSIVO_R, TIPO_OPERAZIONE_R, STATO_PRC_R, TIMESTAMP_PRC_R, ID_ORDINE_R,
				NUMERO_FASE, CODICE_FASE, R_RISORSA, R_OPERAZIONE, DESCRIZIONE_R, TEMPO_PREP, UM_TMP_PREP, TEMPO_UNITARIO, UM_TMP_UNITARIO, TIPO_TEMPO,
				R_FORNITORE, TIPO_LAV, NUM_RITORNO, R_ANNO_ORD, R_NUMERO_ORD, R_RIGA_ORD, R_RIGA_RISORSA, R_OPERAZ, R_ATTIVITA, TIPO_RISORSA_PAN,
				LIV_RISORSA_PAN, R_RISORSA_PAN, PART_PROGRAM, PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN, STATO_ATV,
				R_LINEA_PROD
				)
				AS
				(
				SELECT
				T.ID_AZIENDA, T.ID_AMBIENTE_NIC, T.ID_PROGRESSIVO, T.GRUPPO, T.TIPO_OPERAZIONE, T.STATO_PRC, T.TIMESTAMP_PRC, T.TIPO_ORDINE,
				T.ID_ORDINE, T.ID_MAGAZZINO, T.ID_ARTICOLO, T.ID_VERSIONE, T.ID_CONFIGURAZIONE, T.ID_COMMESSA, T.ID_CLIENTE, T.DESCRIZIONE,
				T.DATA_FINE_RCS, T.QTA_ORD_UM_PRM, T.R_UM_PRM_MAG, T.STATO_ORDINE,
				R.ID_PROGRESSIVO, R.TIPO_OPERAZIONE, R.STATO_PRC, R.TIMESTAMP_PRC, R.ID_ORDINE,
				R.ID_FASE, R.CODICE_FASE, R.R_RISORSA, R.R_OPERAZIONE, R.DESCRIZIONE, R.TEMPO_PREP, R.UM_TMP_PREP, R.TEMPO_UNITARIO, R.UM_TMP_UNITARIO, R.TIPO_TEMPO,
				R.R_FORNITORE, R.TIPO_LAV, R.NUM_RITORNO, R.R_ANNO_ORD, R.R_NUMERO_ORD, R.R_RIGA_ORD, R.R_RIGA_RISORSA, R.R_OPERAZ, R.R_ATTIVITA, R.TIPO_RISORSA_PAN,
				R.LIV_RISORSA_PAN, R.R_RISORSA_PAN, R.RIF_PART_PROGRAM, R.PRIORITA_LISTA_ATV, LISTA_ATV_ASSEGN, R.STATO_ATV,
				A.R_LINEA_PROD
				FROM
				THIP.NIC_ORDESE_ATV R
				JOIN THIP.NIC_ORD_ESEC T ON
				(R.ID_AZIENDA = T.ID_AZIENDA AND R.ID_AMBIENTE_NIC = T.ID_AMBIENTE_NIC AND R.ID_ORDINE = T.ID_ORDINE)
				JOIN THIP.ARTICOLI A ON
				(T.ID_AZIENDA = A.ID_AZIENDA AND T.ID_ARTICOLO = A.ID_ARTICOLO)
				)

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BYYEAV3 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BYYEAV3' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BYYEAV3 AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.DIFANRFD,
    T1.DIFNRPEA,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.T79IMUOP,
    T1.T79IMOFC,
    T1.ENCPRDIC,
    T1.ENCPRDOC,
    T1.DICIMUTI
FROM FINANCE.BYYEAPT T1
