Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36920/tddml/SOGG_GRP_MKTG_SQL_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.SOGG_GRP_MKTG_SQL_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.SOGG_GRP_MKTG_SQL_V01 

	(ID_AZIENDA, PROGRESSIVO, ID_GRP_MKTG, TP_SOGGETTO, ID_SOGGETTO, ID_CLIENTE, ID_FORNITORE, ID_AGENTE, ID_DIPENDENTE, ID_ANAGRAFICO, ID_CONTATTO, DENOMINAZIONE, EMAIL, TELEFONO, CELLULARE, FAX, INDIRIZZO, 
	LOCALITA, CAP, R_NAZIONE, NAZ_DESCR, R_PROVINCIA, PROV_DESC, R_ZONA, ZONA_DESC, R_MICROAREA, MICRO_DESC, R_PROVENIENZA, 
	PROVEN_DESC, RESPONSABILE, RESP_DESC, CATEGORIA, CAT_DESC, AGENTE, AG_DESC, SITO_WEB, ATTIVA_RUB, NOTE, R_ANAGR_RUBR, R_RUBRICA)

	AS

	SELECT  SOG.ID_AZIENDA, 
		SOG.PROGRESSIVO, 
		SOG.ID_GRP_MKTG, 
		SOG.TP_SOGGETTO, 
		CLI.ID_CLIENTE,
		CLI.ID_CLIENTE,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CLI.RAGIONE_SOCIALE,
		CASE WHEN SOG.R_RUBRICA IS NOT NULL THEN RUB.IND_EMAIL ELSE CLI.IND_EMAIL END,
		CASE WHEN SOG.R_RUBRICA IS NOT NULL THEN RUB.NUM_TELEFONO ELSE CLI.NUM_TELEFONO END,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(20)),
		RUB.NUM_FAX,
		CLI.INDIRIZZO,
		CLI.LOCALITA, 
		CLI.CAP, 
		CLI.R_NAZIONE, 
		NAZ.T34DSNOR, 
		CLI.R_PROVINCIA,
		PRV.T35DSNOR,
		CLI.R_ZONA,
		ZONA.T31DSNOR,
		CLI.R_MICROAREA,
		MIC_CLI.T54DSNOR,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(3)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CLI.R_RESPON_VENDITE, 
		RESP_VEN.DESCRIZIONE,
		CLI.R_CAT_VEN_CLI,
		CAT_VEN.DESCRIZIONE,
		CLI.R_AGENTE,
		AGN.DESCRIZIONE,
		CLI.SITO_INT,
		SOG.ATTIVA_RUBRICA, 
		SOG.NOTE,
		SOG.R_ANAGR_RUBR,
		SOG.R_RUBRICA

	     FROM THIP.SOGGETTI_GRUPPI_MKTG SOG
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CLI_VEN_V01 CLI ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = SOG.ID_AZIENDA AND
			CLI.ID_CLIENTE = SOG.ID_SOGGETTO
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT34PT NAZ ON 
			CLI.R_NAZIONE = NAZ.T34CD 			
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT35PT PRV ON 
			CLI.R_NAZIONE = PRV.T34CD AND 
			CLI.R_PROVINCIA = PRV.T35CD 
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT31PT ZONA ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = ZONA.T01CD AND      
			CLI.R_ZONA = ZONA.T31CD
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT54PT MIC_CLI ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = MIC_CLI.T01CD AND      
			CLI.R_MICROAREA = MIC_CLI.T54CD
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RESPON_VENDITE RESP_VEN ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = RESP_VEN.ID_AZIENDA AND      
			CLI.R_RESPON_VENDITE = RESP_VEN.ID_RESPON_VENDITE
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CAT_VEN_CLI CAT_VEN ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = CAT_VEN.ID_AZIENDA AND      
			CLI.R_CAT_VEN_CLI = CAT_VEN.ID_CAT_VEN_CLI
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.AGENTI AGN ON 
			CLI.ID_AZIENDA = AGN.ID_AZIENDA AND      
			CLI.R_AGENTE = AGN.ID_AGENTE
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RUBRICA_V01 RUB ON 
			RUB.ID_ANAGRAFICO = SOG.R_ANAGR_RUBR AND 
			RUB.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB = SOG.R_RUBRICA 
	
	WHERE SOG.TP_SOGGETTO = '1'

UNION 
	SELECT 
		SOG.ID_AZIENDA, 
		SOG.PROGRESSIVO, 
		SOG.ID_GRP_MKTG, 
		SOG.TP_SOGGETTO, 
		FORN.ID_FORNITORE,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		FORN.ID_FORNITORE,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),		
		FORN.RAGIONE_SOCIALE,
		CASE WHEN SOG.R_RUBRICA IS NOT NULL THEN RUB.IND_EMAIL ELSE FORN.IND_EMAIL END,
		CASE WHEN SOG.R_RUBRICA IS NOT NULL THEN RUB.NUM_TELEFONO ELSE FORN.NUM_TELEFONO END,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(20)),
		RUB.NUM_FAX,
		FORN.INDIRIZZO, 
		FORN.LOCALITA, 
		FORN.CAP, 
		FORN.R_NAZIONE, 
		NAZ.T34DSNOR, 
		FORN.R_PROVINCIA,
		PRV.T35DSNOR,
		FORN.R_ZONA,
		ZONA.T31DSNOR,
		FORN.R_MICROAREA,
		MIC_FOR.T60DSNOR,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(3)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		FORN.R_RESPON_ACQUISTO, 
		RESP_ACQ.DESCRIZIONE,
		FORN.R_CAT_ACQ_FOR,
		CAT_ACQ.DESCRIZIONE,
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(3)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		FORN.SITO_INT,
		SOG.ATTIVA_RUBRICA, 
		SOG.NOTE,
		SOG.R_ANAGR_RUBR,
		SOG.R_RUBRICA


	     FROM THIP.SOGGETTI_GRUPPI_MKTG SOG

		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FOR_ACQ_V01 FORN ON 
			FORN.ID_AZIENDA = SOG.ID_AZIENDA AND
			FORN.ID_FORNITORE = SOG.ID_SOGGETTO

		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT34PT NAZ ON 
			FORN.R_NAZIONE = NAZ.T34CD 
			
		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT35PT PRV ON 
			FORN.R_NAZIONE = PRV.T34CD 
			AND FORN.R_PROVINCIA = PRV.T35CD 

		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT31PT ZONA ON 
			FORN.ID_AZIENDA = ZONA.T01CD AND      
			FORN.R_ZONA = ZONA.T31CD

		LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBT60PT MIC_FOR ON 
			FORN.ID_AZIENDA = MIC_FOR.T01CD AND      
			FORN.R_MICROAREA = MIC_FOR.T60CD

		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RESPON_ACQUIS RESP_ACQ ON 
			FORN.ID_AZIENDA = RESP_ACQ.ID_AZIENDA AND      
			FORN.R_RESPON_ACQUISTO = RESP_ACQ.ID_RESPON_ACQUIS

		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CAT_ACQ_FOR CAT_ACQ ON 
			FORN.ID_AZIENDA = CAT_ACQ.ID_AZIENDA AND      
			FORN.R_CAT_ACQ_FOR = CAT_ACQ.ID_CAT_ACQ_FOR

		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RUBRICA_V01 RUB ON 
			RUB.ID_ANAGRAFICO = SOG.R_ANAGR_RUBR AND 
			RUB.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB = SOG.R_RUBRICA 

	WHERE SOG.TP_SOGGETTO = '2'

		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),
		CAST (NULL AS CHAR(35)),

		RTRIM(CAST(ANAGR.ID_ANAGRAFICO AS CHAR)),

		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RUBRICA_V01 RUB ON

			RUB.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB = SOG.R_RUBRICA 

	WHERE SOG.TP_SOGGETTO = '3'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37334/tddml/ORDVEN_RIG_TES_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.ORDVEN_RIG_TES_V01
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.ORDVEN_RIG_TES_V01 AS 
	
SELECT 
    T.DATA_ORDINE     AS DATA_ORDINE, 
    T.NUMERO_ORD_FMT  AS NUMERO_ORD_FMT, 
    T.R_CLIENTE       AS R_CLIENTE, 
    T.R_VALUTA        AS R_VALUTA, 
    T.R_CAU_ORD_VEN   AS R_CAU_ORD_VEN, 
    T.R_MOD_PAGAMENTO AS R_MOD_PAGAMENTO, 
    T.R_DIVISIONE     AS R_DIVISIONE, 
    
    T.R_AGENTE           AS R_AGENTE_TES, 
    T.R_AGENTE_SUB       AS R_AG_SUB_TES, 
    T.R_RESPON_VENDITE   AS R_RESP_VEN_TES, 
	A.R_MACROFAMIGLIA AS R_MACROFAMIGLIA, 
	A.R_MICROFAMIGLIA AS R_MICROFAMIGLIA, 
	A.R_SUBFAMIGLIA AS R_SUBFAMIGLIA, 
	A.R_LINEA_PROD AS R_LINEA_PROD,
    R.*
    
FROM 
    THIP.ORD_VEN_RIG R, 
    THIP.ORD_VEN_TES T,
    THIP.ARTICOLI A 
    
WHERE 
    T.ID_AZIENDA        = R.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND R.ID_ANNO_ORD   = T.ID_ANNO_ORDINE 
    AND R.ID_NUMERO_ORD = T.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
    AND R.STATO         = 'V' 
    AND T.STATO         = 'V'
    AND A.ID_AZIENDA    = R.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND A.ID_ARTICOLO   = R.R_ARTICOLO
GRANT ALL ON THIP.ORDVEN_RIG_TES_V01 TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37333/tddml/BBANIPTV1.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBANIPTV1
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBANIPTV1 AS
	SELECT  BBANAPT.*,BBANIPT.ANACD AS BBANIPT_ANACD, BBANIPT.ANICD AS BBANIPT_ANICD, BBANIPT.ANIRASOC AS BBANIPT_ANIRASOC, 
  	BBANIPT.ANIRASO2 AS BBANIPT_ANIRASO2, BBANIPT.ANIINDIR AS BBANIPT_ANIINDIR, BBANIPT.ANIINDI2 AS BBANIPT_ANIINDI2, 
  	BBANIPT.ANILOCAL AS BBANIPT_ANILOCAL, BBANIPT.T34CD AS BBANIPT_T34CD, BBANIPT.T35CD AS BBANIPT_T35CD,
  	BBANIPT.ANICAP AS BBANIPT_ANICAP,BBANIPT.ANITELEF AS BBANIPT_ANITELEF, BBANIPT.ANITELEX AS BBANIPT_ANITELEX, 
  	BBANIPT.ANIFAX AS BBANIPT_ANIFAX, BBANIPT.ANICOEDI AS BBANIPT_ANICOEDI, BBANIPT.ANIININT AS BBANIPT_ANIININT, 
  	BBANIPT.ANINOTEL AS BBANIPT_ANINOTEL, BBANIPT.DIZSTATO AS BBANIPT_DIZSTATO,
  	BBANIPT.TIMESTAMP_AGG AS BBANIPT_TIMESTAMP_AGG,BBAN1PT.ANALATI AS BBANIPT_LAT ,BBAN1PT.ANALONGI AS BBANIPT_LONG,BBAN1PT.ANALATI,BBAN1PT.ANALONGI
        ,BBANIPT.ANIIPEC AS BBANIPT_ANIIPEC ,BBANIPT.ANIDFPA AS BBANIPT_ANIDFPA   	
	FROM 
		FINANCE.BBANAPT  BBANAPT 
  	INNER JOIN FINANCE.BBANIPT BBANIPT
		ON  BBANAPT.ANACD=BBANIPT.ANACD 
	LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BBAN1PT BBAN1PT 
		ON BBANAPT.ANACD = BBAN1PT.ANACD AND 
		BBANIPT.ANICD  = BBAN1PT.ANICD

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37570/primrose/script/02BCFPRVG.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCFPRVG
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCFPRVG ( 
    PZSTATO, 
    PZNRAZIO, 
    PZDTAZIO, 
    PZUSAZIO, 
    PZHINVIO, 
    PZKHFATT, 
    PZHBODYF, 
    PZTIPODC, 
    PZAMBNTE, 
    PZDATADC, 
    PZNUMDOC, 
    PZCLIFOR, 
    PZSTATOE, 
    PZGESTIO, 
    PZERRINT, 
    PZDTAPRT, 
    PZUSERPR, 
    PZCLSPRT, 
    PZTIPOPR, 
    PZANNOPR, 
    PZNUMPRT, 
    PZTIPOCF, 
    PZSETGES, 
    PZUTEGES, 
    PZDTACCE, 
    PZUTEACC, 
    PZDTCONT, 
    PZUTECNT, 
    PZTIPORG, 
    PZNUMREG, 
    PZDTREGC, 
    PZTIPOCT, 
    PZDTARCH, 
    PZUTEARC, 
    PZTIPOAR, 
    PZSTATOP, 
    PZIDDOCR, 
    PZDTDOCR, 
    PZCODCUP, 
    PZCODCIG, 
    PZTOTDOC, 
    PZCALDOC, 
    PZTOTPAG, 
    PZCALCPAG, 
    PZNOMXML, 
    PZDTRICE, 
    PZORARIC, 
    PZDTSTAT, 
    PZFMTTRA, 
    PZCODDST, 
    PZNOTFAT, 
    PQCAUS, 
    P2CODICE, 
    P2CFISCA, 
    P2DENOM, 
    P2COGN, 
    P2NOME, 
    P2SINDI, 
    P2SNCIV, 
    P2SCOMU, 
    P2SPROV, 
    P2SCAP, 
    T02CD, 
    T22CD, 
    T07CD, 
    MOVNPIVA, 
    MOVDTRCO, 
    PZFILLR1, 
    PZFILLR2, 
    T01CD, 
    FPRICORC, 
    FPRICOEL, 
    FPRFL1,
	FPRDINTE
) AS 
SELECT 
    PZ_STATO, 
    PZ_NRAZIONE, 
    PZ_DTAZIONE, 
    PZ_USAZIONE, 
    PZ_KEYPRGINVIO, 
    PZ_KEYHEADERFATT, 
    PZ_KEYBODYFATT, 
    PZ_TIPODOC, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    CAST(PZ_DATA AS DATETIME), 
    PZ_NUMERO, 
    PZ_CLIFOR, 
    PZ_STATOELAB, 
    PZ_GESTIONE, 
    PZ_ERRINT, 
    PZ_DATAPROT, 
    PZ_USERPROT, 
    PZ_CLASPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOPROT, 
    PZ_ANNOPROT, 
    PZ_NUMPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOCF, 
    PZ_SETGEST, 
    PZ_UTEGEST, 
    PZ_DATAACCET, 
    PZ_UTENACCET, 
    PZ_DATACONT, 
    PZ_UTENCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOREGCONT, 
    PZ_NUMREGCONT, 
    PZ_DATAREGCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOCONT, 
    PZ_DATAARCH, 
    PZ_UTENARCH, 
    PZ_TIPOARC, 
    PZ_STATOPROT, 
    PZ_CODSDI, 
    PZ_DATADOCR, 
    PZ_CODCUP, 
    PZ_CODCIG, 
    COALESCE(PQ_IMPTOTDOC, 0), 
    PZ_IMPCALDOC, 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPONIBILE_FATTURA, 0), 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPOSTA_FATTURA, 0), 
    PZ_NOMXML, 
    PZ_DATAORARIC, 
    PZ_DATAORARIC, 
    PZ_DATASTATO, 
    PZ_FMTTRASMISS, 
    PZ_CODDEST, 
    PZ_NOTAFATT, 
    COALESCE(PQ_CAUSALE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_FISCIVACOD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_CODFISCALE, ' '), 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ')<>' ') THEN COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ') 
      ELSE SUBSTRING(RTRIM(P2_ANACOGNOME)+' '+RTRIM(P2_ANANOME), 1, 80) END 
     ), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANACOGNOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANANOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEIND, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDENRCIVICO, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECOMUNE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEPROV, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECAP, 0), 
    COALESCE(T02CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T22CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T07CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(MOVNPIVA, 0), 
    COALESCE(MOVDTRCO, PZ_DATAREGCONT), 
    PZ_FILLER1, 
    PZ_FILLER2, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='A') THEN 'A'  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='U') THEN 'U'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='P') THEN 'I'
      WHEN (PZ_ERRINT<>' ') THEN 'E'  
      ELSE 'V'  END
     ) AS FPRICORC, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATOPROT='3') THEN 'R'  
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='C') THEN 'C'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='P') THEN 'P'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='E') THEN 'E'
      WHEN (PZ_CLIFOR=' ') THEN 'F' 
      ELSE 'T'  END
     ) AS FPRICOEL,      
     ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(T5.ALLEGATI_PRESENTI, ' ')='Y') THEN '1'  
      ELSE '0'  END
     ) AS FPRFL1,
	( CASE
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD16') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD17') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD18') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD19') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD20') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD21') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD22') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD23') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD27') THEN '1'
	ELSE '0' END
	) AS FPRDINTE
FROM  THIP.FPPRO00F 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAA2700F ON 
    PQ_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    PQ_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    PQ_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
INNER JOIN THIP.PAA0200F ON 
    P2_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    P2_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    P2_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMOTPT ON 
    T01CD=PZ_AMBIENTE AND 
    T09CD=PZ_TIPOREGCONT AND 
    MOVNUREG=PZ_NUMREGCONT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T5 ON 
    T5.KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    T5.KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    T5.KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCFPRVG TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37659/tddml/RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    RICH.* , 
    CASE(STATO_RICHIESTA) 
        WHEN 'C' 
        THEN DATEDIFF(dd,COALESCE(DATA_RICHIESTA_CLI, DATA_RICH),(DATA_CHIUSURA)) 
        ELSE DATEDIFF(dd,COALESCE(DATA_RICHIESTA_CLI, DATA_RICH),CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
    END AS GIORNI_RICH_PEND 
FROM 
    THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO RICH

		THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.ID_AZIENDA AS ID_AZIENDA,

		FROM THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR, THIP.RISORSE 
		WHERE THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.ID_AZIENDA = THIP.RISORSE.ID_AZIENDA 
		AND THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.TIPO_RISORSA = THIP.RISORSE.TIPO_RISORSA

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37826/primrose/script/02BCFPRVG.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCFPRVG
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCFPRVG ( 
    PZSTATO, 
    PZNRAZIO, 
    PZDTAZIO, 
    PZUSAZIO, 
    PZHINVIO, 
    PZKHFATT, 
    PZHBODYF, 
    PZTIPODC, 
    PZAMBNTE, 
    PZDATADC, 
    PZNUMDOC, 
    PZCLIFOR, 
    PZSTATOE, 
    PZGESTIO, 
    PZERRINT, 
    PZDTAPRT, 
    PZUSERPR, 
    PZCLSPRT, 
    PZTIPOPR, 
    PZANNOPR, 
    PZNUMPRT, 
    PZTIPOCF, 
    PZSETGES, 
    PZUTEGES, 
    PZDTACCE, 
    PZUTEACC, 
    PZDTCONT, 
    PZUTECNT, 
    PZTIPORG, 
    PZNUMREG, 
    PZDTREGC, 
    PZTIPOCT, 
    PZDTARCH, 
    PZUTEARC, 
    PZTIPOAR, 
    PZSTATOP, 
    PZIDDOCR, 
    PZDTDOCR, 
    PZCODCUP, 
    PZCODCIG, 
    PZTOTDOC, 
    PZCALDOC, 
    PZTOTPAG, 
    PZCALCPAG, 
    PZNOMXML, 
    PZDTRICE, 
    PZORARIC, 
    PZDTSTAT, 
    PZFMTTRA, 
    PZCODDST, 
    PZNOTFAT, 
    PQCAUS, 
    P2CODICE, 
    P2CFISCA, 
    P2DENOM, 
    P2COGN, 
    P2NOME, 
    P2SINDI, 
    P2SNCIV, 
    P2SCOMU, 
    P2SPROV, 
    P2SCAP, 
    T02CD, 
    T22CD, 
    T07CD, 
    MOVNPIVA, 
    MOVDTRCO, 
    PZFILLR1, 
    PZFILLR2, 
    T01CD, 
    FPRICORC, 
    FPRICOEL, 
    FPRFL1,
	FPRDINTE
) AS 
SELECT 
    PZ_STATO, 
    PZ_NRAZIONE, 
    PZ_DTAZIONE, 
    PZ_USAZIONE, 
    PZ_KEYPRGINVIO, 
    PZ_KEYHEADERFATT, 
    PZ_KEYBODYFATT, 
    PZ_TIPODOC, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    CAST(PZ_DATA AS DATETIME), 
    PZ_NUMERO, 
    PZ_CLIFOR, 
    PZ_STATOELAB, 
    PZ_GESTIONE, 
    PZ_ERRINT, 
    PZ_DATAPROT, 
    PZ_USERPROT, 
    PZ_CLASPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOPROT, 
    PZ_ANNOPROT, 
    PZ_NUMPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOCF, 
    PZ_SETGEST, 
    PZ_UTEGEST, 
    PZ_DATAACCET, 
    PZ_UTENACCET, 
    PZ_DATACONT, 
    PZ_UTENCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOREGCONT, 
    PZ_NUMREGCONT, 
    PZ_DATAREGCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOCONT, 
    PZ_DATAARCH, 
    PZ_UTENARCH, 
    PZ_TIPOARC, 
    PZ_STATOPROT, 
    PZ_CODSDI, 
    PZ_DATADOCR, 
    PZ_CODCUP, 
    PZ_CODCIG, 
    COALESCE(PQ_IMPTOTDOC, 0), 
    PZ_IMPCALDOC, 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPONIBILE_FATTURA, 0), 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPOSTA_FATTURA, 0), 
    PZ_NOMXML, 
    CONVERT(DATETIME, CONVERT(DATE, PZ_DATAORARIC)), 
    PZ_DATAORARIC, 
    PZ_DATASTATO, 
    PZ_FMTTRASMISS, 
    PZ_CODDEST, 
    PZ_NOTAFATT, 
    COALESCE(PQ_CAUSALE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_FISCIVACOD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_CODFISCALE, ' '), 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ')<>' ') THEN COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ') 
      ELSE SUBSTRING(RTRIM(P2_ANACOGNOME)+' '+RTRIM(P2_ANANOME), 1, 80) END 
     ), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANACOGNOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANANOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEIND, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDENRCIVICO, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECOMUNE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEPROV, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECAP, 0), 
    COALESCE(T02CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T22CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T07CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(MOVNPIVA, 0), 
    CONVERT(DATETIME, CONVERT(DATE, COALESCE(MOVDTRCO, PZ_DATAREGCONT))), 
    PZ_FILLER1, 
    PZ_FILLER2, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='A') THEN 'A'  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='U') THEN 'U'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='P') THEN 'I'
      WHEN (PZ_ERRINT<>' ') THEN 'E'  
      ELSE 'V'  END
     ) AS FPRICORC, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATOPROT='3') THEN 'R'  
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='C') THEN 'C'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='P') THEN 'P'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='E') THEN 'E'
      WHEN (PZ_CLIFOR=' ') THEN 'F' 
      ELSE 'T'  END
     ) AS FPRICOEL,      
     ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(T5.ALLEGATI_PRESENTI, ' ')='Y') THEN '1'  
      ELSE '0'  END
     ) AS FPRFL1,
	( CASE
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD16') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD17') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD18') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD19') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD20') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD21') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD22') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD23') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD27') THEN '1'
	ELSE '0' END
	) AS FPRDINTE
FROM  THIP.FPPRO00F 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAA2700F ON 
    PQ_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    PQ_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    PQ_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
INNER JOIN THIP.PAA0200F ON 
    P2_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    P2_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    P2_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMOTPT ON 
    T01CD=PZ_AMBIENTE AND 
    T09CD=PZ_TIPOREGCONT AND 
    MOVNUREG=PZ_NUMREGCONT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T5 ON 
    T5.KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    T5.KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    T5.KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCFPRVG TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THIP.HISTORY
(
   USER_ID CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(500),
   URL VARCHAR(1000) NOT NULL,
   PARAMS TEXT
)  ON 'THIP8'

GRANT ALL ON THIP.HISTORY TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37860/tddml/VARIAZCST_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V01 AS SELECT ARTCOS.*, ART.ID_ARTICOLO AS R_ARTICOLO, ART.TIPO_PARTE, ART.R_LINEA_PROD AS R_LINEA_PRODOTTO, ART.R_MACROFAMIGLIA, ART.R_MICROFAMIGLIA, ART.R_SUBFAMIGLIA, ART.R_CLASSE_MERCLG, ART.R_CLS_MATERIALE, ART.R_PIANIFICATORE , ART.R_GRP_PRODOTTO , ART.R_CLASSE_FISCALE , ART.R_CLASSE_A , ART.R_CLASSE_B , ART.R_CLASSE_C , ART.R_CLASSE_D , ART.R_CLASSE_E 
FROM THIP.ARTICOLO_COSTI ARTCOS JOIN THIP.ARTICOLI ART ON ( ARTCOS.ID_AZIENDA = ART.ID_AZIENDA AND ARTCOS.ID_ARTICOLO = ART.ID_ARTICOLO )

UPDATE THERA.CLASSRD_ROW 	 
			SET CD_NAME ='Descrizione.Descrizione' , CORR_CLASS_NAME ='DescrizioneInLingua' , CORR_ATTR_NAME ='Descrizione'
			WHERE DEF_SEARCH = 'Y' AND 
			CONCAT(LTRIM(RTRIM(CLASS_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(RELATION_NAME))) IN (SELECT CONCAT(LTRIM(RTRIM(CLASS_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(RELATION_NAME)))  FROM THERA.CLASSRD WHERE CORR_CLASS_NAME = 'UbicazioneLL')

CREATE TABLE THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS
(
   DATA_ORIGIN CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   RUN_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ROW_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   RUN_ACTION CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'I',
   TRASF_STATUS CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DESCR_RIDOTTA CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   DESCRIZIONE VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL,
   STATO CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   ID_ARTICOLO CHAR(25) NOT NULL,
   ID_ASS_IVA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_NAZIONE CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_CONNOTAZ_OSS CHAR(5) NOT NULL
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CM_ART_REG_OSS_I01 ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS (DATA_ORIGIN ASC, RUN_ID ASC, ROW_ID ASC)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CM_ART_REG_OSS_I02 ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS (DATA_ORIGIN ASC, RUN_ID ASC, ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_ARTICOLO ASC, ID_ASS_IVA ASC, ID_NAZIONE ASC, ID_CONNOTAZ_OSS ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS ADD PRIMARY KEY  (DATA_ORIGIN, RUN_ID, ROW_ID)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS TO PUBLIC

ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCF9TPT ADD    PZTIPODC CHAR(4) DEFAULT ' '
UPDATE FINANCE.BCF9TPT SET PZTIPODC =' ' WHERE PZTIPODC IS NULL OR PZTIPODC =''
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


UPDATE FINANCE.BCF9TPT 
			SET FINANCE.BCF9TPT.PZTIPODC = (SELECT B.F9ICSOS FROM THIP.F9IVA00K B WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.T01CD=B.F9ICSOC AND 
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9PIDPAC = B.F9IIDLA AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IIDFI = B.F9IIDFI AND 
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INDOC = B.F9INDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IUDOC = B.F9IUDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9ICREG = B.F9ICREG AND
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INPRI = B.F9INPRI)
			WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.PZTIPODC=' ' AND EXISTS(SELECT * FROM THIP.F9IVA00K C WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.T01CD=C.F9ICSOC AND
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9PIDPAC = C.F9IIDLA AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IIDFI = C.F9IIDFI AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INDOC = C.F9INDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IUDOC = C.F9IUDOC)
#WARNING#
No rows found, the update is failed.


GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCF9TPT TO PUBLIC

    T1.T01CD,

    T1.F9TINTRIC,
    T1.F9IIDFI,

FROM FINANCE.BCF9TPT T1
